Amalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yaseWales axhalabile ukuba el azakuchazwa njengeMuppets
Amalungu aliqela eNdlu yePalamente aye abonisa ukucaphuka xa kucetywa ukuba igama lakhe litshintshwe libe yiMVP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Le mpikiswano ivela kwisicwangciso sokutshintsha igama le ndibano libe yiPalamente yaseWales.
Amalungu endlu yowiso-mthetho kuwo onke amaqela ezopolitiko aye abonisa inkxalabo yokuba eli nyathelo linokuba sisithuko.
Ilungu leqela leqela lezabasebenzi liye lathi iqela lalo lalikhathazwa kukuba i-MWP ithetha nge-Twp okanye i-Pwp.
Kubafundi abangengomaWelsh: NgesiWelsh, i-twp ithetha isidenge kwaye, pwp, isidumbu.
Ilungu leNdibano yePlaid Cymru liye lathi iqela lakhe lonke "aliyiboni kakuhle" kwaye licebise iindlela ezahlukeneyo.
Ngokwabo, ilungu lase Wales elihlala lilinye lathi iqela lalo libonakala lihle kakhulu xa liguqula igama, kodwa lathi kukho umahluko omncinci kakhulu phakathi kwegama elithi MWP kunye nelithi Muppet.
Kule meko, kufuneka kuthiwe unobumba w ngesiWelsh uvakala ngendlela efanayo nonobumba u ngesiNgesi saseYorkshire.
NgokweKomiti yeNdibano ejongene nokwenza isicatshulwa somthetho sokungenisa utshintsho lwamagama: Isigqibo sokugqibela malunga naziphi na iziqinisekiso zokubiza amalungu eNdibano ngokuqinisekileyo siya kuba ngamalungu ngokwawo.
UMthetho kaRhulumente waseWales ka-2017 unika iNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yaseWales amandla okutshintsha igama layo.
NgoJuni, ikomiti yapapasha iziphumo zophando loluntu ngeziphakamiso, kunye nenkxaso ebanzi kwisindululo sokutshintsha igama lendibano libe yiPalamente yaseWales.
Ngokubhekiselele kwisihloko samalungu endlu yowiso-mthetho, nangona ikomiti yakhetha Amalungu ePalamente yaseWales okanye WPM, ukhetho lweMWP lolona lwafumana inkxaso ebanzi kwiphulo loluntu.
Kubonakala ngathi amalungu endlu yowiso-mthetho acebisa iindlela ezahlukeneyo, kodwa ukuzama ukufikelela kwisivumelwano kusenokuba yintlekele kuMongameli weNdlu, uElin Jones, ekulindeleke ukuba abhale umthetho ophuculweyo kwiiveki ezimbalwa ezizayo.
Umthetho ophathelele iinguqu uya kuquka nezinye iinguqu ezinxulumene nokusebenza kwegqiza, njengemigaqo ephathelele ekungafanelekeni kwamalungu alo kunye noyilo lwenkqubo yekomiti.
Amalungu endlu yesigqeba aya kugqiba ngokuvota ngegama lawo ngexesha lengxoxo-mpikiswano enxulumene nomthetho.
Abemi baseMacedonia bavota kwireferendamu yokutshintsha igama lelizwe labo
Abemi baya kukhetha ngeCawa ukuba bayafuna na ukutshintsha igama lelizwe labo libe yi Republic of North Macedonia.
Olu dliwano-ndlebe lwasetyenziswa ukuzama ukusombulula imbambano esusela kumashumi eminyaka neGrisi, esele ineliphondo elibizwa ngokuba yiMakedoni.
I-Athene kudala igxininisa kwinto yokuba igama lommelwane wayo osemaNtla limele indlela yokufuna umhlaba wayo kwaye iphinde yachasana neenzame zelizwe ukuba libe yinxalenye ye-EU ne-NATO.
Umongameli waseMakedoni, uGyorge Ivanov, owaphikisana nenkomfa yokutshintsha igama, wathi uza kuyityeshela le voti.
Noko ke, abo bakwicala elilungileyo, njengoMphathiswa Omkhulu uZoran Zaev, bathi ukutshintsha igama nje kuphela yintlawulo ekufuneka ihlawulwe ukuze ube lilungu le-EU ne-NATO.
Iintsimbi zeSt. Martin's ziyeka ukuvakala: iingxaki zecawa zaseHarlem
"Ngokwembali, abantu abadala endithethe nabo bathi kwakukho ibar necawa kwikona nganye", utshilo uMnu. Adams.
Namhlanje, akukho namnye kubo.
Ngokuka-Adams, ukuphelelwa kweebhari kunokuqondwa.
Uthi, "Abantu banendlela eyahlukileyo yokuhlalisana namhlanje".
"Iindawo zokutyela aziseyiyo loo ndlela yokuma kwegumbi lokuhlala kwindawo apho abantu babehlala khona".
Ngokuphathelele iicawa, ixhalabile kukuba imali efunyenwe ngokuthengisa izinto aziyi kuhlala ixesha elide njengoko bekucingelwa ziinkokeli zazo - yaye ziya kubuya apho zivela khona.
Uthi iicawa zinokutsalwa zizakhiwo zezindlu ezihlala abantu abangenakuzinceda iicawa eziseleyo.
Uthi, "Inkoliso yabantu abathenga izindlu ezihlala abantu abaqhelekileyo, iya kuba ngabamhlophe, ngoko ke, baza kukhawuleza bavale zonke iicawa, kuba akunakwenzeka ukuba abantu abaninzi abafudukela kwezi zindlu babe ngamalungu ezi cawa".
Zombini iicawa zakhiwa ngamabandla amhlophe ngaphambi kokuba iHarlem ibe yidolophu emnyama; iCawa yeMetropolitan Community ngowe-1870 neSt. Martin's kwiminyaka elishumi kamva.
Ibandla lamaWesile elimhlophe elalikho ekuqaleni lahamba ngeminyaka yee-1930.
Ibandla labantsundu elalikwicala elikufutshane lathenga loo mhlaba.
ISt. Martin's yawela ezandleni zebandla elimnyama elalikhokelwa nguReverend John Howard Johnson, owalathisa ukuvalwa kwevenkile kwi-125th Street, enye yezona ndawo ziphambili zorhwebo eHarlem, ezazingafuni ukuqesha okanye ukukhuthaza abantu abamnyama.
Ngowe-1939, umlilo wabangela umonakalo omkhulu kwisakhiwo, yaye xa abafundisi bakaReverend Johnson benza izicwangciso zokuyakha kwakhona, yaba kulapho baqala khona ukwenza umsebenzi wokuthwala.
Umfundisi uDavid Johnson, unyana kaJohnson onguYise kunye nomlandeli wakhe kwicawa yaseSt. Martin's, ngokuzingca wachaza le nqwelo njenge "iikhalori zabantu abahlwempuzekileyo".
Ingcali eyabangela ukuba le nqwelo-mafutha idlalwe ngoJulayi yathi: "Yinto exabisekileyo kwinkcubeko" yaye "yisenzo esingenaxabiso kwimbali".
Ingcali, uTiffany Ng waseYunivesithi yaseMichigan, waphawula ukuba le yayiyindawo yokuqala ehlabathini apho kwakusetyenziswa khona imvumi engumntu omnyama, uDionisio A. Lind, owafudukela kwindlu enkulu yaseRiverside Church kwiminyaka eli-18 eyadlulayo.
Ngokutsho kukaMnu Merriweather, uSt. Martin akazange amthathe indawo yakhe.
Oko kuye kwavakala eSt. Martin's kwezi nyanga zidluleyo, ngokuchaseneyo, ibe yimbali enzima yabayili bezakhiwo nabaqulunqi, abanye babo beqhutywa ziinkokeli zecawa nezinye ze-episcopal diocese.
Ibhunga, elilawulayo kwiphondo, elinabakhokeli becawa, labhalela i-diocese ngoJulayi ophelileyo livakalisa inkxalabo yalo yokuba i-diocese ifuna ukudlulisela iindleko kwibhunga, nangona eli lokugqibela lingazange libandakanyeke ekuqeshweni kwezakhiwo kunye nabanikezeli beenkonzo ababethunyelwe yi-diocese.
Abanye abefundisi baye bakhalaza ngokungabikho kokungafihli nto kwibhunga.
