Umntwana oneminyaka eli-13 ubudala wahlaselwa waza wonzakala ngumtyhalanga ngeMigqibelo ngoxa wayehamba efuna amaqwarhashe eKhalifoniya ngosuku lokuqala lonyaka wamaqwarhashe, ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni.
