Peter Jones furious emva kokuba uHolly Willoughby ehlele emva kwesivumelwano se-GBP 11 million
Inkwenkwezi yeDragons' Den uPeter Jones washiya furious emva kokuba umbonisi weTV uHolly Willoughby wabuya kwisivumelwano se-GBP 11 yezigidi kunye neshishini lokuthengisa uphawu lobomi bukaJones ukugxila kwiikontraki zakhe ezintsha kunye neMarks and Spencer kunye ne-ITV.
UWilloughby akanalo ixesha lokuzinikela kwishishini lezinto zasekhaya kunye nezixhobo zeTruly.
Ishishini lale mibini yabasasazi lalinganiswa neGoop brand kaGwyneth Paltrow.
Umqhubi we-This Morning, oneminyaka engama-37 ubudala, wasebenzisa i-Instagram ukubhengeza umhlala-phantsi wakhe.
UHolly Willoughby ushiye inkwenkwezi yeDragons' Den uPeter Jones enomsindo ngokurhoxa ngomzuzu wokugqibela kwishishini elidibeneyo lokuvelisa uphawu lokuzonwabisa ukuze agxile kwiikontraki zakhe ezintsha kunye neMarks & Spencer kunye ne-ITV, ezaziza kumenza afumane inzuzo enkulu.
Ngokutsho kwemithombo eyahlukeneyo, uJones "wacaphuka" xa inkwenkwezi ebomvu yethelevishini yavuma, ngexesha lentlanganiso ebinzima ebibanjelwe ngoLwesibini kwikomkhulu lobukhosi bayo eMarlow, eBuckinghamshire, ukuba izivumelwano ezintsha ze-host, ezixabisa i-1.5 yezigidi ze-GBP, zithetha ukuba akasayi kuba nexesha elaneleyo lokuzinikela kwi-truly brand ye-household and accessories.
Eli shishini lalingathi lifaniswa neGoop brand kaGwyneth Paltrow kwaye lalizama ukuphinda kabini ubutyebi bukaWilloughby, obuqikelelwa kwi-11 yezigidi ze-GBP.
Xa uWilloughby, oneminyaka engama-37 ubudala, wasebenzisa i-Instagram ukubhengeza ukuhamba kwakhe eTruly, uJones wathatha inqwelomoya yabucala esinge kwenye yeendawo zakhe zokuhlala ngaphandle kwe-UK.
Ngokutsho komnye umthombo, uTruly wayeyeyona nto iphambili kuHolly.
Yayimiselwe ukuba ibe likamva lakhe elide nalapho wayeza kubonakala khona kwiminyaka engama-20 okanye engama-30 ezayo.
Isigqibo sakhe sokuyeka sasishiya onke amaqela achaphazelekayo engakwazi ukuthetha.
Akukho mntu wakholwa koko kwenzekayo ngoLwesibini, sasisondele kakhulu ekuqaliseni...
Ngoku kukho indawo yokugcina impahla eMarlow esembindini wayo elungele ukuthengiswa.
Ngokutsho kweengcali, ukushiya inkwenkwezi ye-This Morning, enye yeenkwenkwezi ezifumana imali eninzi e-UK, kunokubiza izigidi kwinkampani ngenxa yotyalo-mali olukhulu olwenziwe kwiimveliso, ukusuka kwiipads kunye neepals ukuya kwiimpahla kunye neengubo zasekhaya, kunye nokuthintelwa kokukhutshwa kwayo.
Ukongezelela, kusenokuthetha ukuphela kobuhlobo obude.
Umama wabantwana abathathu uWilloughby nomyeni wakhe uDan Baldwin babenolwalamano olusenyongweni noJones nomfazi wakhe uTara Capp kangangeminyaka elishumi.
UWilloughby waseka iTruly kunye noCapp ngo-2016, yaye uJones, oneminyaka engama-52 ubudala, wajoyina njengosihlalo kulo nyaka uphelileyo.
Bobabini ababini bachitha iholide kunye. Ukongeza, uJones unelungelo le-40% kwi-Baldwin's TV Production.
UWilloughby uza kuba ngummeli we-M&S olandelayo kwaye uza kuthatha indawo ka-Ant McPartlin njengombonisi we-ITV's I'm A Celebrity.
Umthombo osondele kuJones uthe izolo "asizukuthetha ngeshishini lakhe".
