Kutheni uTrump eye wayeka kangaka?
UTrump wathi, ecaphula ilizwi lomntu obhala iindaba:
Andincamanga kwanto.
Wabona ukuba uKim unomdla wokubamba intlanganiso yesibini emva kokuba intlanganiso yokuqala eyayibanjelwe eSingapore ngoJuni yabhengezwa njengenyathelo elikhulu lokuya kwi-denuclearization yaseNyakatho Korea.
Nangona kunjalo, iingxoxo malunga nokukhutshwa kwe-nuclear zimi.
Emva kweenyanga ezintathu kwindibano yeengqungquthela eyayibanjelwe eSingapore, ummeli omkhulu waseMntla Korea uRi Yong Ho wathi kwiinkokeli zeNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo ngoMgqibelo ukuba uMntla Korea awuboni "impendulo ebhaliweyo" evela e-US kwimizamo yokuqala yokulwa izixhobo eyenziwe lilizwe lakhe.
Noko ke, waphawula ukuba, i-US iyaqhubeka nokusebenzisa izigwebo ngenjongo yokugcina uxinzelelo.
Isigqibo sikaTrump, nangona kunjalo, sasinethemba kakhulu kwintetho yakhe.
"Senza kakuhle kakhulu neNorth Korea", watsho.
Sasiza kuhlasela uMntla Korea.
Kwakuza kufa izigidi zabantu.
Kwaye ngoku sinalo ulwalamano olukhulu.
Ngokutsho kukaTrump, imigudu yakhe yokuphucula ubudlelwane noKim iye yavelisa iziphumo ezilungileyo: ukupheliswa kovavanyo lweemisila, uncedo ekukhululeni amabanjwa nokubuyela ekhaya kwintsalela yamajoni aseMerika.
Kwaye wayikhusela indlela yakhe engaqhelekanga yokuthetha noKim.
"Kulula kakhulu ukuba ngumongameli, kodwa endaweni yokuba abantu abali-10,000 bazame ukungena kule ndawo igcwele abantu, bekuya kuba nama-200", utshilo uTrump, ebhekisa kwindimbane eyayiphambi kwakhe.
Isiqithi esonakeleyo, amawaka ebulawa yitsunami neenyikima eIndonesia
Emva kwenyikima yaseLombok, umzekelo, imibutho engekho phantsi korhulumente kwamanye amazwe yaxelelwa ukuba ayimfuneko.
Nangona abantu abangaphezu kwe-10% baseLombok kwafuneka bafuduke, akukho ntlekele yesizwe eyabhengezwa, imfuneko yangaphambili ukuze kukhutshwe uncedo lwamazwe ngamazwe.
"Ngelishwa, kwiimeko ezininzi, baye benza kwacaca ukuba abafuni uncedo lwamazwe ngamazwe, ngoko ke imeko inzima kakhulu", utshilo uSumbung.
Nangona iSave the Children iqhuba iqela eliya ePalu, akukacaci ukuba abantu basemzini bangakwazi na ukusebenza kwelo lizwe.
Umkhulumeli we-arhente yeentlekele zikazwelonke, uMnu Sutopo, wathi amagosa aseIndonesia ayevavanya imeko ePalu ukuze abone ukuba ingaba amaziko ehlabathi avunyelwe na ukuba ancedise xa kunikwa uncedo.
Ngenxa yeenyikima ezihlala zisenzeka eIndonesia, ngelishwa eli lizwe lisengxakini ngenxa yomsindo wendalo.
Nangona iitsunami zenziwe eAceh, azikho kwezinye iindawo.
Ukungabikho kwee-siren ezixwayisayo ePalu xa kukho itsunami, nangona kwakukho isilumkiso esisemthethweni, kusenokwenzeka ukuba kwaba negalelo ekubulaweni kwabantu.
Ukuhamba phakathi kweziqithi ezininzi zaseIndonesia, kunzima, ubuncinane.
Iintlekele zemvelo zenza kube nzima ngakumbi ukufikelela.
Inqanawa yesibhedlele eyayibambeke eLombok ukuze inyamekele amaxhoba enyikima ngoku iya ePalu; nangona kunjalo, kuya kuthatha ubuncinci iintsuku ezintathu ukufika kwindawo yentlekele entsha.
UMongameli Joko Widodo wayejonge ukuphucula iziseko ezisemgangathweni zaseIndonesia njengento ephambili kwiphulo lakhe lonyulo, yaye uye watyala imali eninzi kwiindlela zikaloliwe.
Noko ke, urhulumente kaJoko uza kuphinda akhethwe kunyaka ozayo ngenxa yokungabikho kwemali.
Kwakhona uJoko ujongene noxinzelelo lweengxabano eziqhubekayo zamahlelo kweli lizwe, apho amalungu amaSilamsi amaninzi aye amkela inkolo yokugcina ingqibelelo.
