Ingulube Ebulalayo Ibulala Umfama WaseTshayina
Umfama wahlaselwa waza wabulawa yingulube kwimarike ekumazantsi-ntshona eChina, ngokutsho kweengxelo zasekuhlaleni.
Le ndoda, ekuthiwa nguYuan, yafunyanwa ifile, inesifo esibangelwa kukuchithwa kwegazi kufuphi nendawo ekuthengiswa kuyo iihagu eLiupanshui kwiphondo laseGuizhou, njengoko iSouth China Morning Post yaxela ngeCawa.
NgoMeyi 30, 2005, umfuyi wehagu wayelungiselela ukufaka isitofu seentshulube kwifama yaseXining, kwiPhondo laseQinghai, eTshayina.
Kuthiwa, ngoLwesithathu, yena nomza wakhe basuka kwiphondo elikufutshane laseYunnan besiya kuthengisa iihagu ezili-15 emarikeni.
Ngentsasa elandelayo, umzala wakhe wamfumana efile waza wafumanisa ucango olungavulekanga olwalukhangele kwifama yehagu eyayikufuphi.
Ngokutsho kwakhe, enkundleni kwakukho ihagu enkulu eyindoda enegama eligazi.
Uxilongo lwe-forensic lwangqina ukuba i-garry ye-250 kg yayenzakalise umfama, ngokutsho kwengxelo.
"Umzala wam wayeneenyawo ezaphukileyo, ezigcwele igazi", watsho umzala, ogama linguWu, njengoko kukhankanyiwe kwiindaba zangokuhlwa zaseGuyang.
Iifoto ezirekhodiweyo zeekhamera zokhuseleko zibonisa u-Yuan engena emarikeni ngo-4:40 kusasa ngoLwesine ukuze ondle iihagu.
Umzimba wakhe wafunyanwa malunga neyure kamva.
Isilwanyana esabulala le ndoda sasingeyompahla kaYuan okanye umza wakhe.
Omnye wabaphathi bevenkile wathi kwiindaba zengokuhlwa ukuba le ngulube yahlala itshixiwe yaza yabekelwa bucala ukuze ingakwazi ukuhlasela abanye, ngoxa amapolisa ayeqokelela ubungqina kwindawo yesigameko.
Kuthiwa, intsapho kaYuan kunye nabaphathi bevenkile bathethathethana ngokufumana imbuyekezo ngenxa yokufa kwakhe.
Nangona zingaqhelekanga, kuye kwabhalwa amatyala okuhlasela kwehagu.
Ngowe-2016 ingulube yahlasela ibhinqa nomyeni walo kwifama yabo eMassachusetts, ishiya indoda enamanxeba amaninzi.
Kwiminyaka elishumi ngaphambi koko, ihagu elingu-300 kg lahlasela umfama waseWales kwiitrektara zakhe de umfazi wakhe wakwazi ukuyothusa.
Emva kokuba umfama waseOregon watyiwa ziingulube zakhe ngo-2012, umfama waseManitoba waxelela iCBC News ukuba iihagu azidli ngokuba ndlongondlongo kodwa incasa yegazi inokuba yinto eyenza ukuba ingulube ibe nenkani.
Bathanda ukudlala.
Banjengabantwana, banomdla kakhulu, abafuni kwenza nto imbi.
Kufuneka nje sibanike imbeko abayifaneleyo, utshilo.
Iinxalenye zeNkanyamba uRosa ziya kuzisa imvula enzima kumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States
Ngokutsho kweenkcukacha-manani, iNkanyamba uRosa iye yaba buthathaka njengoko iqukuqela phezu kwamanzi abandayo kunxweme olusemantla eMexico.
Noko ke, iRosa iza kunisa imvula enzima kumntla weMexico nakumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo.
U-Rosa wayenomoya we-138 km/h, owawufana nesaqhwithi esingumgangatho wokuqala, ngo-5:00 kusasa ngeCawa, ixesha laseMpuma eUnited States, yaye wahlala kumgama oziikhilomitha ezingama-620 kumzantsi-ntshona wePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
I-Rosa kulindeleke ukuba iye ngasentla ngeCawa.
Ngelo xesha, i-Pacific Ocean Depression isenza umonakalo, isenza ukuba i-Eurasia ifuduke iye ngasempuma ukuya kunxweme olusentshona lwe-United States.
I-Rosa iza kunika imvula engange-250mm kwezinye iindawo eMexico ngoMvulo.
Emva koko, ukufuma kweetropiki kuya kunxibelelana nokudodobala okusondelayo ukuze kuvelise imvula enzima ebanzi kulo lonke umzantsi-ntshona kwiintsuku ezizayo.
Kwiindawo ezininzi, imvula engama-25 ukuya kuma-100 mm iya kubangela imvula eyingozi, ukugeleza kwenkunkuma kunye nokwenzeka kokugungxulwa komhlaba entlango.
Ukufuma okuqinileyo kweetropiki kuya kubangela amazinga emvula aphantse abe ngama-50 ukuya kuma-75 mm ngeyure kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo, ngakumbi kwiindawo ezisemazantsi eNevada naseArizona.
Kulindeleke imvula engama-50 ukuya kuma-100 mm kwiindawo ezisezantsi-ntshona, ingakumbi kwindawo enkulu yaseArizona.
Kukho ithuba lokuba kuya kubakho imilambo, kuba imeko iya isiba mandundu ngokukhawuleza ngenxa yokungasebenzi kakuhle kwemvula.
Akucetyiswa kwaphela ukungena entlango ngeenyawo xa kukho isoyikiso semvula yeetropiki.
Imvula enzima inokubangela ukuba imifula ibe ngamanzi angakwaziyo ukulawula, yaye iziqhwithi zinokuzisa imimoya engqongqo namafu othuli kwiindawo ezithile.
Ukuwa kweMvula kuza kunika imvula enzima kwiindawo ezithile ezikunxweme olusemazantsi eKhalifoniya.
Kusenokwenzeka ukuba kuqhume imvula engaphezulu kwe-50 mm, nto leyo enokubangela ukuba kubekho imvula encinane kunye neendlela ezinamabala.
Oku kuya kuba yimvula yokuqala yexesha lemvula kulo mmandla.
Iimvula eziqengqelekayo ziya kuqala ukuza eArizona phakathi kobusuku bangoMvulo nangoMvulo kusasa, ngaphambi kokuba imvula ibe yeyona ixhaphakileyo phakathi kobusuku bangoMvulo nangoLwesibini.
Imvula enzima iza kusasazeka kummandla weCantoned Four ngoLwesibini ize iqhubeke yonke le ntsasa.
Ngo-Oktobha, kuya kubakho ukuguquguquka okukhulu kwamaqondo obushushu kulo lonke elaseUnited States njengoko iArctic iphola, nangona iitropiki ziya kuhlala zishushu.
Le nto inokubangela ngamanye amaxesha utshintsho olukhulu lobushushu kumgama omfutshane.
Ingingqi esembindini weUnited States ngeCawa ngumzekelo ocacileyo wolu hlanga lweemeko zobushushu ezihluke kakhulu.
Kukho umahluko wobushushu ophantse ube ngama-20 degrees phakathi kweKansas City, eMissouri, neOmaha, eNebraska, naphakathi kweSt. Louis neDes Moines, eIowa.
Kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo, ubushushu obuqhubekayo behlobo buya kuzama ukwanda kwakhona.
Kuqikelelwa ukuba kuya kuqalisa u-Oktobha kushushu kwimimandla emininzi embindini nasempuma ye-USA, amaqondo obushushu ajikeleze ama-27 degrees ukusuka kummandla wase-South Plains ukuya kwiindawo ezikuMntla-mpuma.
Isixeko saseNew York sinokuba nama-27 degrees ngeCawa, nto leyo enokuba ngama-10 degrees ngaphezulu komlinganiselo.
Ngokutsho kwengxelo yemozulu yexesha elide, kukho amathuba amaninzi okuba amaqondo obushushu aphezulu kunesiqhelo aya kuba sempuma eUnited States kwisiqingatha sokuqala senyanga ka-Oktobha.
Bangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 ababukeli ababukele ingxelo kaBrett Kavanaugh
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele ubungqina obumangalisayo ngoLwesine bomntu oza kuba ngumviwa kwiNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh kunye nebhinqa elathi lamtyhola ngokumxhaphaza ngokwesondo, ekuthiwa kwenzeka kwiminyaka yoo-1980, uChristine Blasey Ford.
Ngelo xesha, kwakusekho imeko yepolitiki, apho amajelo eendaba aphazamiseka kwiinkqubo zawo zemihla ngemihla zangoLwesihlanu ngenxa yenguqu yemizuzu yokugqibela: isivumelwano esenziwe yiSenator yaseArizona uJeff Flake sokuba iFBI iqhube uphando ngeza zityholo kangangeveki.
UFord uchazele iKomiti yezeNkundla yeSenate ukuba wayeqinisekile ukuba uKavanaugh wayemchukumise enxilile waza wazama ukumkhulula kwiqela lesikolo.
UKavanaugh, kwiingxelo zakhe ezizukileyo, wathi wayeqinisekile ukuba oku akuzange kwenzeke.
Ngokutsho kukaNielsen, kusenokwenzeka ukuba bangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20.4 ababukeli ababukele le ngxelo ngoLwesihlanu.
Le nkampani yayine-avareji yababukeli be-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kunye ne-MSNBC.
Amanani abaphulaphuli ayengafumaneki ngoko nangoko kwezinye iinkqubo ezazisasaza ubungqina, njengePBS, C-SPAN okanye iFox Business Network.
Ukongeza, uNielsen udla ngokuba neengxaki xa ebala abantu abambonayo eofisini yakhe.
Xa ujonga ngenyameko, le ngqokelela ifana neqela labalandeli beqela lezemidlalo okanye leqela labalandeli beqela leOscar.
I-Fox News Channel, iinkokeli zayo ezivelele eziye zaxhasa ukubekwa kukaKavanaugh, yaba yeyona ntetho ibonwa kakhulu, nge-avareji ye-5.69 yezigidi zabalandeli ngexesha lobungqina bemini yonke, ngokutsho kukaNielsen.
I-ABC yaba sesibini ngezigidi ezingama-3.26 zabukeli.
I-CBS yafumana i-3.1 yezigidi, i-NBC 2.94 yezigidi, i-MSNBC 2.89 yezigidi kunye ne-CNN 2.52 yezigidi, ngokwedatha yeNielsen.
Umdla uhlala uphezulu emva kwengxelo.
UFlake wayengumntu ophambili kumdlalo weFriday.
Emva kokuba i-ofisi ye-moderate Republican ikhuphe ingxelo isithi iza kuvota uKavanaugh, uFlake wabanjwa kwiikhamera ze-CNN ne-CBS ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu ngelixa wayehlaselwa ngabaqhankqalazi xa wayezama ukunyuka kwi-elevator ukuya kwi-Judicial Affairs Committee.
UFlake wahlala imizuzu eliqela engaboni kakuhle ngelixa wayebuyiselwa kwiTV ephilayo kwiCNN.
"Ndilapha phambi kwakho", watsho omnye umfazi.
Ngaba ucinga ukuba uthetha inyani kweli lizwe?
Bathi kuye, 'unamandla, kanti baninzi abafazi abangenalo!'
UFlake uthe iofisi yakhe ikhuphe ingxelo kwaye, phambi kokuba iingcango zonyuko zivaliwe, wathi unezinto ezininzi aza kuzithetha kwiKomiti.
Kwiiyure ezimbalwa, zonke iinkqubo ze-cable kunye ne-broadcast zazisasaza bukhoma ixesha apho iKomiti yezeNkundla yayiza kuvota ukuba ingaba iyaqhubeka okanye ayiyi kuqhubeka nokumiselwa kukaKavanaugh kwi-Senate epheleleyo ukuze ithumele ivoti.
UFlake uthe, endaweni yoko, uza kwenza oko kuphela xa eqonda ukuba i-FBI iza kuphanda izityholo ezichasene nomntu ozakuqokwa kwiveki ezayo, into efunwa yinxalenye encinane yamaDemocrats.
UFlake waqiniseka ngenxa yeengxoxo awayenayo nomhlobo wakhe, uSenator weDemokhrasi uChris Coons.
Emva kwengxoxo kamva noCoons kunye nabanye abasenathi, uFlake wenza isigqibo sakhe.
Inketho ekhethwe nguFlake yayinefuthe, kuba kwakubonakala ukuba amaRiphabliki awazukufumana amavoti aneleyo okuxhasa uKavanaugh ngaphandle kophando.
UMongameli Trump uvule uphando lwe-FBI ngezimangalo ezibhekiselele kuKavanaugh.
