Kwintetho eyongezelelweyo noMay kwiphepha eliphambili, owayesakuba nguMphathiswa Wezangaphandle kaMay uBoris Johnson, waqinisa ukuhlasela kwakhe kwinto ebizwa ngokuba sisicwangciso seChequers seBrexit, apho athi ukuba i-UK ne-EU bahlawule irhafu kunye ngokungaqondakaliyo.
Ukubulawa kukaWayde Sims: Amapolisa abamba umsolwa uDyteon Simpson ngokubulawa komdlali weqela leLSU
Amapolisa abambe umntu ekuthiwa ubetha ngemipu umbulali kaWayde Sims, umdlali webasketball oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala owayesakuba kwiqela leLSU.
UDyteon Simpson, oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala, ubanjiwe waza wathunyelwa entolongweni ngenxa yokubulala umntu kwinqanaba lesibini, ngokutsho kweSebe lePolisa laseBaton Rouge.
Amagosa apapasha ividiyo eboniswayo ebonisana uSims noSimpson.
Amapolisa afumana ezi glasi kwindawo yesiganeko, athi afumane iDNA kaSimpson kuzo, ngokutsho kweWAFB.
Emva kokubuza uSimpson, wavuma ukuba umbulale ngepistol, ngokutsho kwamapolisa.
