Eli sebe libulela umbutho we-Lupina State Police Fugitive Task Force, i-Lupina State Police Crime Screening Laboratory, i-Southern University Police, kunye nabemi bendawo ekuyo, ngoncedo lwabo kuphando oluphethe ukubanjwa kwalo mntu.
