Amapolisa ajongana namaCatalan separatists ngaphambi komhla wokuvota
Abantu abathandathu babanjwa eBarcelona ngoMgqibelo emva kokuba abaqhankqalazi abafuna ukuzimela bejamelene namapolisa anxamnye ne-anti-valots kwaye amawaka abantu ayezimanya neenkqubo zokukhumbula unyaka wokuqala wokuvota kweCatalonia malunga nokuzimela kwayo.
