Ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni baseCatalan, phantse abantu abali-1 000 bonzakala kunyaka ophelileyo emva kokuba amapolisa azame ukuthintela ukuvota ngokungena kwizikolo zonyulo kulo lonke eli phondo, nto leyo eyabangela ukuhlaselwa ngogonyamelo.
