Amagosa ayefuneka ukuba ancediswe ngenxa yamanxeba amancinci ebusweni kwindawo yesenzo.
Ngokutsho komkhokeli wentolongo, "Sithumele abasebenzi abaqeqeshwe ngokukhethekileyo ukuba bazame ukusombulula ingxaki esele iqhubeka kwintolongo yaseLong Martin.
Abasebenzi abathandathu baye kwafuneka bancedwe ngenxa yokwenzakala.
Siyaqonda ukuba abo babangele le ngxabano baza kujamelana neengxaki ezinzulu, ibe basenokuchitha ixesha elingakumbi entolongweni.
Kwindawo yentolongo yaseLong Lartin kukho amabanjwa angaphezu kwama-500, kuquka amanye awona manyala ayingozi.
NgoJuni, kwavakala ukuba umphathi wentolongo kwafuneka ancedwe esibhedlele emva kokuhlaselwa lelinye ibanjwa.
Ukongezelela, ngo-Oktobha wonyaka ophelileyo, amagosa okulwa neentlawulo aye abonakala ejele ukuze alungise ingxabano enzulu apho abasebenzi basejele babetshayelwa ngeebhola zebhola.
INkanyamba uRosa isongela iPhoenix, iLas Vegas neSalt Lake City ngamanzi amaninzi (iindawo ezinomkhenkce zinokungenelwa)
Akuqhelekanga ukuba i-tropical depression ichaphazele iArizona, kodwa yile nto kanye enokwenzeka ekuqaleni kweveki ezayo xa okuseleyo kwe-Hurricane Rosa kudlula kwintlango esemazantsi-ntshona, kunye nomngcipheko wokuzikhukula.
I-National Weather Service sele ikhuphe izilumkiso zemvula ngoMvulo nangoLwesibini kwintshona yeArizona ukuya kutsho emazantsi nasempuma yeNevada, kumazantsi mpuma eKhalifoniya naseUtah, kuquka izixeko zasePhoenix, eFlagstaff, eLas Vegas naseSalt Lake City.
I-Rosa kulindeleke ukuba ifike ngqo ePhoenix ngoLwesibini ize ifike ngoMvulo ebusuku xa kunetha.
I-National Weather Service yasePhoenix yathi kwi-polling that only two tropical cyclones have maintained the state of storm or tropical depression within a 200-mile radius of Phoenix since 1950.
I-Hurricane Katrina (1967) yahlala kwi-64 km ukusuka kumda we-Arizona.
Iimodeli zakutshanje zeziko lesizwe lezikhukula zibonelela nge-50 ukuya kwi-100mm yemvula, kunye neendawo ezikhethekileyo apho kuya kubhaliswa khona ukuya kuthi ga kwi-150mm eMogollon eArizona.
Ezinye iindawo zasentlango ezisemazantsi ntshona, kuquka iCentral Rockies kunye neGreat Basin, zinokubhala ukusuka kwi-25 ukuya kwi-50 mm, kunye nokwenzeka kweendawo ezizimeleyo ukuya kuthi ga kwi-100 mm.
Kwiindawo ezingaphaya komngcipheko wamanzi, imvula yeRosa isenokuba ziindaba ezimnandi, njengoko lo mmandla unengxaki yokoma.
Nangona imvula ingumbandela onzulu, imvula eninzi inokuba luncedo kakhulu, kuba ummandla osemazantsi-ntshona unxunguphele.
Ngokutsho kwe-US Drought Control Service, ngaphezu kwama-40% e-Arizona inengxaki yembalela, olwesibini ukwanda, ngokutsho kwe-weather.com.
Kodwa kuqala, iNkanyamba uRosa iza kufika kwiNtlambo yaseBaja California, eMexico.
U-Rosa uqhubeke enamandla njengesaqhwithi ngeCawa kusasa, kunye nemimoya ephezulu ye-137 km/h, kwaye ngoku ikumgama we-620 km kumazantsi ePunta Eugenia, eMexico, ihamba ngasentla ngesantya se-20 km/h.
Le nkanyamba iye yafumana amanzi abandayo kwiPasifiki, nto leyo ebangela ukuba ilahlekelwe ngamandla.
Ngoko ke, kulindeleke ukuba ibethe uMexico ibe yingqele yomoya emandundu ngoMvulo okanye ngokuhlwa.
Imvula eninzi kwiindawo ezahlukeneyo eMexico inokuba namandla, ibe kukho umngcipheko omkhulu wezikhukula.
Ngokutsho kweweather.com,  kulindeleke imvula engama-75 ukuya kuma-150 mm ukusuka eBaja California ukuya kumntla-ntshona weSonora, enokwenzeka ukuba ifike kuma-250 mm.
Emva koko, iRosa iza kuya emantla ngeqhwa eMexico, ngaphambi kokuba ifike kumda waseArizona ngentsasa yangoLwesibini ngeqhwa le-tropical depression, ukuze ekugqibeleni iwele i-Arizona ize ifike kumazantsi e-Utah emva kobusuku ngoLwesibini.
"Ingozi ephambili esiyilindeleyo kwiRosa okanye kwinto eseleyo kuyo yimvula enzima kakhulu eBaja California, emantla ntshona eSonora nasentlango ekumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States", ngokutsho kweziko lezikhukhula.
Kucingelwa ukuba le mvula iza kubangela izikhukula eziyingozi nokugcwala kwenkunkuma kumangcwaba, kunye nokuguguleka komhlaba kwiindawo ezisezintabeni.
