Iindidi zabantu ezibulewe yinyikima netsunami eIndonesia
Ubuncinane abantu abangama-384 baye bafa, abaninzi bathathwa ngamaza amakhulu abetha elunxwemeni, ngenxa yenyikima enkulu kunye netsunami ezichaphazele isiqithi saseIndonesia iSulawesi, ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni ngoMgqibelo.
Amakhulu abantu ayehlanganisene ngolwesiHlanu ngenxa yomnyhadala owawuseLwandle kwisixeko sasePalu xa amaza angangeemitha ezintandathu (malunga neemitha ezintandathu) ahlaselwa kunxweme ngobusuku, ekhukulisa abantu abaninzi de bafa yaye esonakalisa yonke into eyayikwindlela yawo.
I-tsunami yalandelwa yinyikima enkulu ye-7.5.
"Xa kwafika isoyikiso sentshonga-mlilo izolo, abantu babesenza imisebenzi yabo elunxwemeni kwaye abazange babaleke ngokukhawuleza, ngoko ke baba ngamaxhoba", utshilo uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, isithethi se-BNPB, isebe lokunciphisa iintlekele, kwincoko eseJakarta.
"Itsunami ayizange ize yodwa, yahudulela iimoto, iziqu, izindlu, yonakalisa yonke into esemhlabeni", watsho uNugroho, wongezelela esithi itsunami yahamba elwandle evulekileyo ngesantya se-800 km/h ngaphambi kokuba ifike kunxweme.
Kukho abantu abakwazile ukunyuka emthini besinda kutsunami baza basinda, utshilo.
Abantu abamalunga ne-16 700 kwafuneka ukuba bagxothwe kwiindawo ezingama-24 ezahlukeneyo ePalu.
Imifanekiso esuka emoyeni epapashwe yiarhente yokunciphisa iintlekele apho kubonwa khona inani leivenkile nezakhiwo ezonakeleyo, iibhulorho eziguqulweyo nezidilikileyo kunye nemosque engqongwe ngamanzi.
Iziqhwithi zaqhubeka ukubetha esi sixeko sinxweme ngoMgqibelo.
Iinyikima ezothusayo zavakala kwindawo enabemi abazizigidi eziyi-2.4.
I-Indonesia's Technology Assessment and Application Agency (BPPT) yathi amandla akhutshwa yinyikima enkulu yangoLwesihlanu, ayephantse aphindwe ka-200 ngamandla ebhombu leathom elaphoswa eHiroshima kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Ngokutsho kwe-Agency, iimpawu zendawo yesixeko, esikwisiphelo sebhadi ende nelincinane, zinokunyusa ngamandla ubukhulu besitsunami.
UNugroho wachaza umonakalo 'njengomkhulu' waza wathi amawaka amakhaya, izibhedlele, iindawo zokuthenga neehotele zawa.
Uthi imizimba yamalungu athile eendonga zafunyanwa phakathi kwezakhiwo ezabhodlozwayo, wongezelela ngelithi abantu abangama-540 bonzakala yaye abangama-29 baphoswa.
Ngokutsho kukaNugroho, abantu abaswelekileyo kunye nomonakalo usenokwanda kunxweme olukude kangangeekhilomitha ezingama-300 kumntla wePalu, ummandla obizwa ngokuba yiDonggala, kufutshane nendawo ekwakusenzeka kuyo inyikima.
Unxibelelwano "lwashiyeka luphelele kwaye ngoko ke akukho lwazi" olwalusuka eDonggala, utshilo uNugroho.
Abantu abangaphezu kwama-300 000 bahlala apho, iRed Cross ithe kwingxelo, yongezelela ngelithi abasebenzi bayo kunye namavolontiya ayeza kuya kwiindawo ezichaphazelekayo.
"Yinto ebuhlungu, kodwa enokwenzeka ukuba ibe mbi kakhulu", utsho.
I-Agency yagxekwa kakhulu ngoMgqibelo ngenxa yokungachazi ukuza kwetsunami ePalu, nangona amagosa athi amaza afika ngexesha lokukhutshwa kwesi silumkiso.
Kwividiyo yomntu othanda izinto ezenzeka emhlabeni, umntu okwizakhiwo eziphakamileyo unokumamela abantu abasesitalatweni bememeza bexwayisa abantu ngetsunami ezayo.
Kwimizuzu nje embalwa, kwaqhuma udonga lwamanzi elunxwemeni, lwaphalaza izakhiwo neemoto.
