Abantu baseMakedoni benza ivoti yokuvota ukuze bagqibe kwelokuba balitshintshe na igama lelizwe
NgeCawa ephelileyo, abantu baseMakedoni babambe irhafu yokutshintsha igama labo libe yiRepublic of North Macedonia, inyathelo elaliza kusombulula imbambano esusela kumashumi eminyaka neGrisi, eyayibhloke izicelo zeMakedoni zokungena kwi-European Union naseNATO.
IGrisi, enesiphaluka esibizwa ngokuba yiMakedoni, ithi igama lommelwane wayo osemntla limela ilizwe layo yaye iye yamthintela ukuba angene kwiNATO nakwi-EU.
NgoJuni, oorhulumente ababini bafikelela kwisivumelwano ngegama elitsha elicebisiweyo, kodwa abachasi besizwe bathi utshintsho luya kubangela ukuba abantu baseMacedonia abangamaSlav babe ngamaxhoba.
Umongameli uGyorge Ivanov uthe akayi kuthatha inxaxheba kwireferendamu, yaye iphulo lokurhoxisa eli libonisa ukuba akunakwenzeka ukuba inani elifunekayo lokuthabatha inxaxheba limalunga nama-50% ukuze le referendum ibe semthethweni.
Umbuzo okhankanywe kwiphepha lereferendum uthi: Ngaba uyavuma ukuba lilungu leNATO ne-EU, ngokuvuma isivumelwano neGrisi?
Abaxhasi bokutshintsha igama, kuquka noMphathiswa Omkhulu uZoran Zaev, bathi lixabiso elifanele ukuhlawulwa ukuze iMakedoni, elinye lamazwe awelayo emva kokwahlukana kweYugoslavia, ingene kwimibutho efana ne-EU ne-NATO.
"Namhlanje ndize kuvota ngekamva lelizwe, ukuze ulutsha lwaseMacedonia luphile ngokukhululekileyo phantsi kweEuropean Union, kuba oko kuthetha ukuba sonke siya kuba nobomi obukhuselekileyo", watsho uOlivera Georgijevska, oneminyaka engama-79, eSkopje.
Nangona ingekho mthethweni, inani elaneleyo lamalungu ePalamente libonakalise ukuba liza kuyithobela imiphumo yokuvota ukuze yenze isigqibo.
Ukutshintsha igama, kufuneka ubuninzi beepesenti ezimbini kwiPalamente.
IKomishoni yoNyulo yeLizwe yachaza ukuba akukho nto ingalunganga eyenzekileyo ngentsimbi yeshumi elinesithathu.
Nangona kunjalo, ukuthatha inxaxheba kwakungama-16%, xa kuthelekiswa nama-34% abhaliswe kunyulo lwakutshanje lwamazwe ngamazwe, olwenziwe ngo-2016, apho ama-66% abantu ababhalisiweyo bavota.
"Ndize kuvota ngabantwana bam, indawo yethu iseYurophu", watsho uGjosze Tanevski, oneminyaka engama-62, kwidolophu elikomkhulu, iSkopje.
