Mhlawumbi ezi zizinto ezinethemba kakhulu kangangamashumi eminyaka, njengoko iBolivia ilinde isigwebo esiza kuziswa yiNkundla Yezizwe Ngezizwe ngo-Oktobha 1 emva kweminyaka emihlanu yokuxoxwa.
URoberto Calzadilla, osisithethi saseBolivia wathi: "Ilizwe laseBolivia linomoya omhle, umanyano noxolo, yaye, akuyomfuneko ukuthi, lilindele isiphumo ngengqondo elungileyo".
