UEvo Morales, umongameli waseBolivia onamava, obhekene nemfazwe yokunyulwa kwakhona kunyaka ozayo, naye unethemba elikhulu kwisigqibo esenziwe ngoMvulo.
"Sisondele kakhulu ekubuyeni kwiPasifiki", wathembisa ngoAgasti ophelileyo.
Noko ke, abanye abahlalutyi bathi akufanelekanga ukuba iNkundla ifune ukuxhasa iBolivia, yaye ukuba ibingenjalo, izinto beziya kuba zimbi kakhulu.
Eli ziko le-UN elise-Netherlands alinagunya lokufumana umhlaba waseChile yaye liqinisekisile ukuba aliyi kuyigqiba into eza kuphumela kwiintetho.
Isigqibo se-TIJ, esiza kwiinyanga ezintandathu kuphela emva kokuba kufakwe izityholo zokugqibela, sibonisa ukuba ityala no lalinzima, utshilo uPaz Zárate, ingcali yelizwe laseChile kumthetho wamazwe ngamazwe.
Yaye kunokuba ibe yimpumelelo, imeko yaseBolivia isenokuba iye yahlehla kule minyaka mine idluleyo.
