"Ukuthetha kukaMorales okulwa kuye kwaphula nayiphi na into eyenziwa yiChile", watsho.
IBolivia neChile ziya kuqhubeka zithetha ngamanye amaxesha, kodwa kuya kuba nzima kakhulu ukugcina incoko emva kwesi siganeko.
La mazwe mabini akakhange atshintshisane ngoonozakuzaku ukususela ngo-1962.
