NgoMvulo ozayo iBolivia iya kuba nethuba elimangalisayo lokuqalisa ixesha elitsha lolwalamano neChile kunye nethuba lokuphelisa ukungavisisani kweminyaka eli-139 kunye nezibonelelo ezinkulu, utshilo.
UCalzadilla waphinda wakhanyela ukuba uMorales, osengomnye wabaongameli abathandwa kakhulu eLatin America, wayesebenzisa umba waselwandle njengendlela yokuphikisana kwezopolitiko.
