John Edward: Iinkcukacha Ngeelwimi Zibalulekile Kubemi Behlabathi
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseSkotlani zigcina umkhondo wokubalaseleyo kwizifundo eziye zaqhubeka ngo-2018 ngenye indlela yeziphumo ezibalaseleyo zeemviwo, eziye zaqiniswa yimpumelelo yomntu ngamnye neyohlangeneyo kwezemidlalo, kwezobugcisa, emculweni nakwezinye iinzame zoluntu.
Ngaphezulu kwama-30,000 abafundi eSkotlani, ezi zikolo, zimelwe liBhunga laseSkotlani leZikolo eziZimeleyo (SCIS) zizama ukubonelela ngenkonzo esemgangathweni kubafundi nakubazali.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zijolise ekulungiseleleni abafundi imfundo ephakamileyo, umsebenzi abawukhethayo, nendawo yabo njengabemi behlabathi.
Njengomzi-mveliso wezemfundo onokukwazi ukuyila nokuqalisa ikharityhulam yesikolo eyenzelwe wena, siyabona ukuba iilwimi zale mihla zisahlala ziyimfundo ekhethwayo nesithandwa kakhulu ezikolweni.
UNelson Mandela wathi, "Ukuba uthetha nomntu ngolwimi aluqondayo, uya kufika entloko.
Ukuba uthetha naye ngolwimi lwakhe, uya kufikelela intliziyo yakhe.
Esi sisikhumbuzo esibalulekileyo sokuba asinakusoloko sithembele kwisiNgesi kuphela ukuba sifuna ukwakha ubudlelwane nokwakha intembelo nabantu bezinye iintlanga.
Ngokweziphumo zonyaka ophelileyo, sibona ukuba iilwimi ziphambili kwizikolo ezizimeleyo.
I-68% yabafundi abafunda iilwimi zasemzini bafumana amanqaku aphezulu.
Idatha, eqokelelwe kwizikolo ezingama-74 ezililungu leSCIS yabonisa ukuba i-72% yabafundi bafumana amanqaku aphezulu kwiMandarin, ngelixa i-72% yabafundi baseJamani, i-69% yabafundi baseFransi kunye ne-63% yabafundi baseSpain bafumana amanqaku aphezulu.
Oku kubonisa ukuba izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseSkotlani zixhasa iilwimi zasemzini njengobuchule obubalulekileyo abantwana nolutsha oluya kubusebenzisa kwixesha elizayo.
Namhlanje, iilwimi, njengesifundo esikhethiweyo, zigcinwa zikwimeko efanayo nezifundo ze-STEM (isayensi, iteknoloji, ubunjineli nezibalo) kwizicwangciso zezifundo ezikumaziko emfundo azimeleyo nakwezinye iindawo.
Uphando olwenziwe ngo-2014 yiKomishoni yezeMisebenzi neZakhono yase-UK lwabonisa ukuba, kwizizathu ezibonelelwa ngabaqeshi zokuba kunzima ukuzalisa izithuba, i-17% yazityala ngokungabi nalwazi lweelwimi.
Ngoko ke, ubuchule beelwimi buya busoloko bubalulekile ekulungiseleleni ulutsha imisebenzi yalo yexesha elizayo.
Njengoko kukho amathuba emisebenzi amaninzi afuna iilwimi, ezi zakhono zibalulekile kwihlabathi eliguquguqukayo.
Nokuba umntu ukhetha yiphi na inkqubela, ukuba ufunde ulwimi lwesibini, uya kuba nelungelo lokwenene kwixesha elizayo xa unobuchule obuhlala buhleli.
Ukukwazi ukunxibelelana ngqo nabantu abavela kwamanye amazwe ngokuzenzekelayo kubeka umntu othetha iilwimi ezininzi phambi kwabo bakhuphisana nabo.
Ngokutsho kophando olwenziwe ngo-2013 ngu-YouGov kubantu abadala abangaphezu kwama-4,000 e-UK, ama-75 ekhulwini abakwazi ukuthetha ulwimi lwangaphandle ngokwaneleyo ukuba bakwazi ukuqhuba incoko, yaye isiFrentshi, esithethwa ngama-15% abantu, lulwimi kuphela olunamanani aphindwe kabini.
Ngenxa yoko, ukutyala imali ekufundiseni iilwimi kubalulekile kubantwana banamhlanje.
Ukwazi iilwimi ezininzi, ingakumbi ezo zikumazwe aphuhlileyo, kuya kunika abantwana amathuba amaninzi okufumana imisebenzi ebalulekileyo.
Izikolo zaseSkotlani ziyahlukahluka ngeelwimi ezifundiswayo.
Ezinye izikolo zijolise kakhulu kwiilwimi zanamhlanje, ngoxa ezinye zifundisa iilwimi ezicingelwa ukuba ziya kubaluleka kwi-UK kwixesha elizayo, malunga ne-2020, njengeMandarin okanye isiJapan.
Nokuba yintoni umntwana wakho ayithandayo, uya kuhlala ekwazi ukukhetha phakathi kweelwimi ezininzi ezikolweni ezizimeleyo, apho kukho abasebenzi abafundisa ngokukhethekileyo kulo mbandela.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseSkotlani zizinikele ekunikeni imeko yokufunda eya kulungiselela abantwana kwaye ibaxhobise ngezakhono ezifunekayo ukuze baphumelele, nokuba kwenzeka ntoni na.
Kwimeko yezorhwebo yehlabathi lonke namhlanje, akukho nto inokuphazanyiswa kukuba iilwimi zisabaluleke kakhulu kwikamva lelizwe, kwaye oku kufuneka kuboniswe kwimfundo.
Enyanisweni, iilwimi zanamhlanje kufuneka ziqwalaselwe njengezi "zakhono zonxibelelwano zamazwe ngamazwe".
Izikolo ezizimeleyo ziya kuqhubeka zinika ukhetho, iyantlukwano, kunye nokugqwesa kulutsha lwaseSkotlani.
Kufuneka uyenze kakuhle.
