ULeBron uza kudlala kwiSan Diego Lakers ngeCawa
Ixesha lokulinda sele liphelile kubaxhasi abafuna ukubona uLeBron James edlala umdlalo wakhe wokuqala kunye neLos Angeles Lakers.
Umqeqeshi weLakers, uLuke Walton, ubhengeze ukuba uJames uza kudlala umdlalo wokuqala wexesha le-pre-season ngeCawa ngokuchasene neDenver Nuggets eSan Diego.
Kodwa imizuzu aza kudlala ngayo isamele igqitywe.
"Kuya kuba ngaphezulu kwe-1 nangaphantsi kwe-48", utshilo uWalton kwiwebhusayithi esemthethweni yeLakers.
Umchola-mlilo weLakers uMike Trudell uthumele kuTwitter esithi uJames uza kudlala imizuzu embalwa.
Emva kokuqeqesha ekuqaleni kwale veki, uJames wabuzwa ngezicwangciso zakhe zokuba neekhalenda zemidlalo emithandathu ye-Lakers.
"Andifuni midlalo yangaphambi kwexesha lonyaka kweli nqanaba lomsebenzi wam ukuze ndikulungele", wabhikisha.
Intlanganiso kaTrump eWest Virginia, Channel YouTube
UMongameli uDonald Trump uqalisa umkhosi wezenzo zenkxaso-nkxaso yakhe ngokuhlwa e Wheeling, eNtshona Virginia.
Le yintlanganiso yokuqala kwezilandelayo ezintlanu ezicwangciselwe uTump kwiveki ezayo, eziquka ukutyelela iindawo ezinomdla, ezifana neTennessee neMississippi.
Ngelixa kuvotelwa ukuqinisekiswa komntu oza kugcwalisa isithuba seNkundla ePhakamileyo, uTrump ufuna ukufumana inkxaso kunyulo oluzayo lwexesha lesiqingatha, njengoko amaRiphabliki enokuba semngciphekweni wokuphulukana nolawulo lweCongress xa kuvotelwa ngoNovemba.
Iphi intlanganiso kaTrump eWest Virginia ngokuhlwa kwaye ungayibukela njani kwi-intanethi?
Intlanganiso kaTrump eWheeling, eNtshona Virginia, imiselwe ukuba ibe ngo-19:00 namhlanje, ngoMgqibelo, Septemba 29, 2018.
Intlanganiso kaTrump eWest Virginia inokubonwa kwi-intanethi kule khonkco ingezantsi, ngokudluliselwa kwevidiyo ebukhoma kwiYouTube.
UTrump usenokuba uza kuqalisa ukuxoxa nomntu oza kuba ngumviwa kwiNkundla Ephakamileyo, uBrett Kavanaugh, ebekade exinezelekile ngenxa yezimangalo zokuxhatshazwa ngokwesondo, njengoko ivoto yokuqinisekiswa kweSenate sele ilinde iveki, kwaye iFBI iphando eli.
Kodwa eyona njongo yale ntlanganiso kukuxhasa amaRepublican akhuphisana kunyulo olucelomngeni lukaNovemba.
Ngoko ke, iintlanganiso ezintlanu zephulo likaMongameli Trump ezicwangciselwe iveki ezayo zijolise ekunyuseni amavolontiya kunye nabaxhasi, ngelixa amaRephabliki ezama ukukhusela nokwandisa ubukhulu bawo kwiNdlu yeeNgwevu nakwiNdlu yabameli, ngokutsho kweReuters.
"Ukulawula iCongress kubaluleke kakhulu kwi-ajenda yakhe kangangokuba umongameli uza kuhamba aye kumazwe amaninzi kangangoko kunokwenzeka, njengoko sihambela kwixesha elixakekileyo lenkqubo", utshilo isithethi sikaTrump esala ukuchazwa, ngokutsho kweReuters.
Le ntlanganiso izakubanjelwa eWesbanco Arena, eWheeling, inokuqokelela abantu baseOhio nasePennsylvania, kwaye izakufumana inkcazelo enkulu kwiindaba zasePittsburgh, ngokutsho kweWest Virginia Metro News.
NgoMgqibelo, kuza kuba sisihlandlo sesibini uTump etyelela eWest Virginia, ilizwe awaphumelela ngalo ngamaphuzu angaphezu kwama-40 ngo-2016.
UTrump uzama ukunceda uPatrick Morrisey, umviwa weRiphabliki kwiSenate yaseWest Virginia, obetha kanobom kwiinkonzo zophando.
"Akusosibonakaliso esihle ukuba uMorrisey uza kunikwa inkxaso kwiinkqubo zophando", utshilo uSimon Haeder, isazi ngezopolitiko kwiYunivesithi yaseWest Virginia, ngokutsho kweReuters.
I-Ryder Cup 2018: Iqela laseMerika libonisa umnqweno walo wokugcina amathemba ephila kwiimidlalo ezizodwa ngeCawa
Emva kweeseshoni ezintathu ezingalinganiyo, i-four-outs ngoMgqibelo emva kwemini mhlawumbi yayiyinto efunekayo kule Ryder Cup.
I-swinging pendulum ye-dynamics yinto eyenziweyo yezemidlalo, apho abadlali bakholelwa ngokwenene, ngakumbi kukhuphiswano olunje.
Ngoko ke, yiyiphi indlela ephumelelayo?
"Baye banamanqaku amathandathu, ngoku bane, ngoko ndicinga ukuba sisemgangathweni omncinci", utshilo uJordan Spieth njengoko wayehamba ekupheleni kosuku.
Ngokucacileyo, iYurophu inenzuzo, inamanqaku amane phambili, inamanqaku ali-12 ngaphezulu.
AmaMerika, njengoko uSpieth esitsho, avakalelwa kukuba umoya uvuthuza kancinci ngakwicala lawo kwaye anezizathu ezininzi zokukhuthazeka, ubukhulu becala ngenxa yemeko yefom kaSpieth noJustin Thomas, abadlale kunye imini yonke kwaye bobabini banamanqaku amathathu kwane.
USpieth uye wabulala ukususela kwitheyi ukuya kumhlaba kwaye ubeka umzekelo.
Iintswahla zokubhiyozela zanda ngamandla njengoko wayeqhubeka nokujikeleza kwakhe kwaye wabeka i-putt ebalulekileyo yokulinganisa umdlalo wesine, xa yena noThomas babephantsi emva kweebhola ezimbini.
Wabhiyozela ukubetha kwakhe okubanike ukuphumelela kumdlalo kwi 15th hole ngesikhalo esifanayo, ngendlela ebonisa ukuba ukholelwa ukuba iqela laseMelika alikaphumeleli kukhuphiswano.
"Kufuneka uzame ngamandla akho onke uze ukhathalele iqela lakho", watsho uSpieth.
Yinto yonke abaseleyo ukuba abadlali ngoku.
18 imingxuma ukuze ushiye uphawu.
Abadlali ababini kuphela abanamanqaku angaphezulu kunaSpieth noThomas kwezi ntsuku zimbini zidlulileyo nguFrancesco Molinari noTommy Fleetwood, umxholo ongathandabuzekiyo weRyder Cup.
Esi sibini sihle kodwa simnandi saseYurophu sinxiba ezine ezine yaye asizenzi iimpazamo.
UMoliwood yayikukuphela kwesibini esingazange senze ibhogi ngoMgqibelo emva kwemini, kwaye sakuphepha ukubheja ngoMgqibelo ekuseni noLwesihlanu emva kwemini, kunye neentsimbi ezisithoba zokugqibela ngoLwesihlanu ekuseni.
Ngenxa yesi siphumo nendlela amandla akhe abonakala ngathi ayahamba ngayo kwiqela eliphithizelayo, kuqinisekiswa ukuba ngabadlali abaza kubetha ngeCawa, kwaye akukho mdlali uthandwa kakhulu kunoFleetwood okanye uMolinari ukuvala uloyiso olunokwenzeka lwaseYurophu ngelixa ilanga litshona kwiLe Golf National.
Ngamana zombini ngexesha elinye kwiimbobo ezahlukeneyo.
Noko ke, ukuthetha ngozuko lwaseYurophu kwakubonakala kungekafiki ixesha.
UBubba Watson noWebb Simpson bakhawuleza baphela nguSergio Garcia, iqhawe le-football yasekuseni, owatshata noAlex Noren.
I-bogey kunye neebini ezimbini kwiimbobo ezisithoba zokuqala zatsho iSpanish neSweden zangena kumngxuma apho zingazange zikwazi ukuphuma.
Kodwa ngeCawa, akukho mntu unokukunceda uphume kuloo mbobo.
Iiforballs kunye neeforums zinomdla kakhulu ekuboneni indlela ezisebenza ngayo ezi zixhobo, iingcebiso ezizinika zona nezingazinikiyo, nendlela isicwangciso-qhinga esinokutshintsha ngayo ngequbuliso.
Ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, iYurophu idlale ngcono njengeqela kwaye iya kujongana nosuku lokugqibela inegunya elibalulekileyo, kodwa le seshoni ye-foursome ibonakalise ukuba iqela laseMelika linomdla wokulwa abanye, ingakumbi eMelika, bebethandabuza.
IYurophu ifikelela kumdlalo wokugqibela weRyder Cup ngamanqaku alungileyo ayi-10-6
IYurophu iza kujamelana nosuku lokugqibela lweRyder Cup inempumelelo emva kokugqiba imidlalo ye-fourball kunye ne-foursomes ngoMgqibelo ngempumelelo eyi-10-6 kwi-United States.
I-duo ephefumlelweyo eyenziwe nguTommy Fleetwood noFrancesco Molinari benza umzamo omkhulu wokufumana uloyiso ezimbini ngokuchasene noTiger Woods obunzima kwaye ushiye irekhodi lakhe, ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, ngamanqaku amane eLe Golf National.
Iqela laseYurophu, elalikhokelwa nguThomas Bjorn, elalifuna ukugcina indebe elalilahlekelwe yiyo kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo eHazeltine, lagqwesa iqela laseMerika elalingekho kakuhle kwimidlalo ye-foortball yasekuseni laza laphakamisa umdlalo nge-3-1.
I-USA yabonisa ukuxhathisa ngakumbi kuma-foursomes yaza yaphumelela imidlalo emibini, kodwa ayizange ikwazi ukunciphisa umahluko.
Iqela likaJim Furyk lalidinga amanqaku asibhozo kwimidlalo eli-12 yodwa ngeCawa ukuze ligcine indebe.
UFleetwood ngowokuqala ukuba ngumdlali wokuqala waseYurophu ukuba aphumelele amanqaku amane alandelelanayo, ngelixa yena noMolinari, owaziwa ngegama elithi Molliwood emva kweveki ephawulekayo, bayisibini sesibini esifumana amanqaku amane kwimidlalo yabo emine yokuqala kwimbali yeRyder Cup.
Emva kokubetha uWoods noPatrick Reed kwii-forballs, bafumana umdlalo omhle wokubetha uWoods ongenayo i-inflation kunye nomdlali wokuqala waseMelika uBryson Dechambeau nge-5&4 eyomeleleyo.
UWoods, owayedlala kwimidlalo emibini ngoMgqibelo, ubonise iziqwenga zobugcisa, kodwa uphulukene nemidlalo eyi-19 kwemi-29 kwi-fourball kunye ne-foursomes, kunye nesixhenxe ngokulandelelana.
UJustin Rose, owayengathathi nxaxheba kwii-forballs zakusasa, waphinda wadibana noHenrik Stenson kwii-foursomes waza wawela kwi-2 ukuya kwi-1 nxamnye noDustin Johnson noBrooks Koepka, ababekwe kwindawo yokuqala neyesithathu kwihlabathi, ngokwahlukeneyo.
Noko ke, iYurophu yayingenalo lonke ithemba ngomhla omnandi, onomoya kumazantsi-ntshona eParis.
UJordan Spieth, oyinkqantosi kathathu kolu khuphiswano, noJustin Thomas bamisela inqaku eliphambili kumaMerika ngoMgqibelo ngokufumana amanqaku amabini.
Bafumana uloyiso ngokuzimisela ngo-2 ukuya ku-1 nxamnye neSpanish uJon Rahm noIan Poulter kwii-fourballs kwaye kamva baphinda baphumelela uPoulter noRory McIlroy ngo-4 ukuya ku-3 kwii-foursomes, emva kokuphulukana nemingxunya emibini yokuqala.
Kuphela ngamaxesha amabini kwimbali yeRyder Cup iqela libuyele kumathuba amane kumdlalo ngamnye, nangona iqela likaFuryk, eliyi-defender, lifuna kuphela ukudibanisa ukugcina.
Nangona kunjalo, emva kokuba ngowesibini ngeentsuku ezimbini, kubonakala ngathi ukuchasana ngeCawa okuzayo kuphantsi kolawulo lwakhe.
I-North Korea ithi ayizukuyekisa ukuzikhusela ngaphandle kokuba kukho umqondiso wokuthembana
UMphathiswa Wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea uxelele iZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ngoMgqibelo ukuba izigwebo eziqhubekayo zandisa ukungathembi kwakhe iUnited States yaye, phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo, ilizwe aliyi kuziphelisa ngaxhatha linye, nangayiphi na indlela, izixhobo zalo zenyukliya.
URi Yong Ho uxelele iNdibano Ebanzi yonyaka ye-UNWTO ukuba iNyakatho Korea ithathe "iindlela ezibalulekileyo zokwenza okuhle" kunyaka ophelileyo, njengokuyeka ukuvavanywa kweentonga zenyukliya, ukucima iziko lokuvavanya i-nuclear, nokuzibophelela ekungaveliseni izixhobo zenyukliya.
"Kodwa ke, asiboni mpendulo evisisana ne-US", utshilo.
"Ngaphandle kokuthembela eMelika, akusayi kubakho kuthembela kukhuseleko lwethu lwesizwe kwaye, phantsi kwezi meko, asiyi kuqalisa ukucima izixhobo ngaxeshanye nangayiphi na indlela".
Nangona uRi wavuma ukukhalaza okuqhelekileyo kweNorth Korea malunga nokumelana kweWashington kwindlela yokucoca i-nuclear ngokwamacandelo apho iNorth Korea yayiza kuvuzwa njengoko ithatha amanyathelo ngokuthe ngcembe, amazwi akhe abonakala ebaluleke kakhulu kuba akazange ayilahle ngokupheleleyo i-nuclear unilateral, njengoko iPyongyang yenzile ngaphambili.
URi wabhekisela kwisibhengezo esidibeneyo esenziwa nguKim Jong Un noDonald Trump kwintlanganiso yokuqala phakathi komongameli osebenza e-US kunye nenkokeli yaseMntla Korea eSingapore ngoJuni 12, apho uKim wazibophelela ekusebenzeni 'kwi-denuclearization ye-Korean Peninsula', ngelixa uTrump wathembisa ukuqinisekisa ukhuseleko lwaseMntla Korea.
INorth Korea iye yazama ukuphelisa iMfazwe yaseKorea yowe-1950-53, kodwa iUnited States iye yazisa ukuba kuqala iPyongyang imele isuse izixhobo zayo zenyukliya.
IWashington iye yazixhathisa izicelo zokuphelisa izohlwayo ezinzima zamazwe ngamazwe ezibekwe phezu kweNorth Korea.
URi uthi, "I-US igxininisa ekubeni kufuneka iqale ngokwenza i-denuclearization ize inyuse uxinzelelo ngezisongelo ukuze iphumelele injongo yayo ngokucinezela, ngaphandle kokuchasa 'ukuvakaliswa kokuphela kwemfazwe.'"
Ingcamango yokuba izohlwayo ziya kusenza siguqe ngamadolo yinto eyenziwa ngabantu abangazi nto ngathi.
Kodwa ingxaki kukuba, izigwebo eziqhubekayo zandisa ukungathembani kwethu.
URi akazange athethe ngecebo lokubamba intlanganiso yesibini phakathi kukaKim noTrump, inkokeli yase-US eyayibethelela kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo ekuqaleni kweveki.
Kunoko, lo mphathiswa wakhankanya iintlanganiso ezintathu phakathi kukaKim kunye nenkokeli yaseMzantsi Korea uMon Jae-in kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo waza wongezelela wathi: Ukuba iqela elibandakanyekayo kumcimbi wokurhoxiswa kwe-nuclear yayinguMzantsi Korea endaweni ye-US, ukucinywa kwe-nuclear kwe-Korean Peninsula ngekungakhange kufikelele kule meko yokuma .
Nangona kunjalo, ithoni yentetho kaRi yahluke kakhulu kwinto awayeyithetha kunyaka ophelileyo, xa waxelela i-UN General Assembly ukuba ukujolisa kwilizwe lase-US ngeemisila zase-North Korea kwakungenakuphepheka emva kokuba uMongameli Mr. Evil Trump ebize uKim ngokuthi Rocket Man kwimisebenzi yokuzibulala.
Ngowama-2008, xa wayeseZizwe Ezimanyeneyo, uTrump, owayesithi ngonyaka ophelileyo uza 'kutshabalalisa' iNyakatho Korea, wancoma uKim ngokuba nesibindi sokuthatha amanyathelo okucima izixhobo, kodwa wathi kusekho umsebenzi omninzi omele wenziwe kwaye izigwebo kufuneka zihlale zikhona de iNyakatho Korea iyenze i-nuclear.
NgoLwesithathu odlulileyo, uTrump wathi akukho xesha limisiweyo lokuyenza loo nto kwaye "ayinamsebenzi nokuba kuthatha iminyaka emibini, emithathu okanye iinyanga ezintlanu".
I-China ne-Russia zithi i-UN Security Council kufuneka imnike umvuzo uPyongyang ngesenzo sakhe.
Noko ke, uMphathiswa Wezangaphandle waseUnited States uMike Pompeo, wathi ngoLwesine kwiBhunga Lezokhuseleko leZizwe Ezimanyeneyo: "Ukusetyenziswa kwezihlwayo zeBhunga Lezokhuseleko kufuneka kuqhubeke ngamandla ngaphandle kokukhetha de siqinisekise ukucinywa ngokupheleleyo kweentonga zenyukliya".
I-UNSC iye yafaka isohlwayo e-North Korea ukususela ngo-2006 kwilinge lokunqanda ukuxhasa ngemali iinkqubo ze-ballistic missile ne-nuclear ze-Pyongyang.
UPompeo wadibana noRi ngaphandle kweNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo kwaye emva koko waxelela ukuba uzakubuya aye ePyongyang kwinyanga ezayo ukulungiselela ingqungquthela yesibini.
UPompeo sele etyelele iNorth Korea kathathu kulo nyaka, kodwa uhambo lwakhe lokugqibela aluzange luhambe kakuhle.
Washiya iPyongyang ngoJulayi esithi kwenziwe inkqubela phambili, kodwa kwiiyure ezimbalwa emva koko, iNorth Korea yamtyhola ngokwenza "iimfuno ezifana nezomntu weqela lezigebenga".
Kwintlanganiso eyayibanjwe noMon kule nyanga, uMntla Korea wathembisa ukudiliza iziko leentolo zeentolo kunye neziko lezinto zenyukliya ukuba iUnited States ithatha "amanyathelo afanelekileyo".
Wathi uKim wamxelela ukuba "iindlela zokuvumelana" ebezifuna zizinto zokhuseleko ezazithenjiswe nguTrump eSingapore, ukongeza kwizenzo zokuzinzisa ubudlelwane neWashington.
Abafundi baseHarvard bafundisa abantu indlela yokuphumla
Kulo nyaka, isifundo esitsha kwiYunivesithi yaseHarvard siye sanceda abafundi baso ukuba balale ixesha elide, ukuze balwe nenkcubeko esasazekayo yokufunda ubusuku bonke, exhokonxwa yicaffeine.
Omnye umphengululi waphawula ukuba abafundi kwiyunivesithi ephambili ehlabathini badla ngokungazi nowathwethwa ngendlela yokuzinyamekela.
UCharles Czeisler, unjingalwazi weNyango yeNgono kwiSikolo seMpilo saseHarvard yaye oyingcali kwiSibhedlele samaBhinqa saseBrigham, wenza le khosi, ekholelwa ukuba yeyokuqala kwezakha zakho eUnited States.
Wafumana inkuthazo yokuyila le khosi emva kokuba ethethe ngentshukumo yokungalali kakuhle.
"Ekupheleni kwale ntetho, intombazana yeza kum yathi, "Kutheni ndixelelwa le nto nje, ndingoyena mfundi uphambili?"
Wathi akukho mntu wakha wamxelela ngokubaluleka kokulala, nto leyo eyandimangalisa, utshilo kwiThe Telegraph.
Kule khosi, eyaqaliswa kulo nyaka, abafundi bafundiswa izinto ezisisiseko ngendlela imikhwa elungileyo yokulala ephucula ngayo impumelelo kwezemidlalo nakwizemfundo, ukongezelela kwimpilo-ntle yabo.
UPaul Barreira, unjingalwazi wezifundo zengqondo kwiHarvard Medical School kunye nomphathi olawulayo weenkonzo zempilo kwiYunivesithi, wathi le yunivesithi yagqiba kwelokuba ifake le khosi emva kokuba ifumene ukuba abanye abafundi babekhathazwa kukulala kakhulu ebudeni beveki.
Le khosi ithatha iyure ibe iquka imisebenzi enokufundwa.
Kwelinye icandelo kukho umfanekiso wegumbi lokulala, apho abafundi kufuneka bacofe iikomityi zekofu, amakhethini, iincam kunye neencwadi ukuze bafumane ulwazi malunga nefuthe lekhowe kunye nokukhanya, indlela ukusebenza kwezemidlalo okuchaphazela ngayo ukungalali, nokubaluleka kokugcina inkqubo yokulala.
Elinye icandelo lafundisa abantu ukuba ukulala ixesha elide kunokubangela isifo sentliziyo, ukuphazamiseka kwengqondo, ukudandatheka nomhlaza.
Emva koko, imephu yekhampasi eneempawu ezinxibelelanayo ikhuthaza abathathi-nxaxheba ukuba bacinge ngendlela abahamba ngayo imihla ngemihla.
Siyazi ukuba indlela abaziphatha ngayo abafundi abayi kutshintsha ngokukhawuleza.
Kodwa sivakalelwa kukuba banelungelo lokwazi, njengokuba benelungelo lokwazi ngemiphumo yokutshaya", utshilo uProfesa Czeisler.
Wathi inkcubeko yokuziphakamisa ngokuhlala ubusuku bonke isekhona, wongezelela esithi ubugcisa bale mihla nengcinezelo ekhulayo kubafundi yenza ukungalali kube yingxaki enkulu.
Walek' umsundulo esithi, ukuqinisekisa ukuba ufumana ubuthongo obufanelekileyo ixesha elide kufanele ukuba ibe sisixhobo esifihlakeleyo sabafundi sokulwa noxinzelelo, ukudinwa nexhala, kwanokuthintela ukwanda komzimba kuba ukungalali kakuhle kubeka ingqondo kwindawo yokungalali kakuhle kwaye kubangela ukuba abafundi bahlale belambile.
URaymond So, umfundi waseCalifornia oneminyaka eli-19 ubudala ofunda iChemistry nePhysical Biology, wanceda uProf. Czeisler ekuyileni le khosi, emva kokuba eye waya kwenye yeeklasi zakhe kunyaka wakhe wokugqibela kunyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.
URaymond wathi le khosi yamvula amehlo yaza yamkhuthaza ukuba ayithengise kwisikolo sonke.
Inyathelo elilandelayo, njengoko enethemba, kukucela abafundi abaphumelele izidanga ukuba benze inkqubo efanayo ngaphambi kokuba bangene kwiziko elikhuphisanayo.
UNjingalwazi Czeisler wacebisa abafundi ukuba bakhumbule ukufaka i-alarm xa belala naxa bevuka, yaye bazi imiphumo eyingozi ye-Blue Light ekhutshwa ziikrini ze-elektroniki nezibane ze-LED, ezinokuphazamisa ukuvisisana kwesingqisho se-circadian yaye zibangele iingxaki zokulala.
