Isitofu esitsha somhlaza sinokufundisa amajoni omzimba ukubona iiseli ezinobungozi
Isitofu esitsha somhlaza sinokufundisa amajoni omzimba ukuba abone aze abulale iiseli ezinobungozi
Isitofu sokugonya sifundisa amajoni omzimba ukuba aqonde iiseli ezinobungozi njengenxalenye yonyango
Le ndlela iquka ukukhupha iiseli zomzimba zomzimba kwisigulana uze uzitshintshe xa uselabhoratri
Unokujonga iproteni eqhelekileyo kumhlaza omninzi uze emva koko uyifake
Uvavanyo lweyeza lokugonya lubonisa iziphumo ezithembisayo kwizigulana ezinamaqela ohlobo lomhlaza.
Elinye ibhinqa elalinikwe isitofu sokubulala iintsholongwane, esifundisa amajoni omzimba ukuba azi iiseli eziyingozi, lafumana isifo somhlaza weqanda esasisele silithabathe iinyanga ezili-18 ukuba liphele.
Le ndlela iquka ukukhupha iiseli zomzimba zomzimba kumguli, ukuzitshintsha elabhoratri ukuze "ubone" iprotein ekhoyo kwiintlobo ezininzi zomhlaza (HER2) uze emva koko uzifake.
UNjingalwazi Jay Berzofsky weNational Cancer Institute eBethesda, eMaryland, eUnited States uthi: "Iziphumo esizifumeneyo zibonisa ukuba sinentsholongwane enethemba".
Iprotein i-HER2  inceda ukukhula kweentlobo ezahlukeneyo zomhlaza, kuquka owamabele, owamaqanda, owempumlo nowomchamo, utshilo uProfesa Berzofsky.
Indlela efanayo yokufumana iiseli zomzimba ezichasene nomhlaza kwizigulana nokufundisa iiseli zomzimba ukuba ziphathe iiseli zomhlaza iye yasebenza kunyango lwe-leukemia.
