I-HIV/AIDS: I-China Ivakalisa Ukwanda Kwabantu AbaneNtsholongwane Nge-14%
I-China iye yachaza ukwanda kwe-14% kwinani labemi abaphila ne-HIV/AIDS.
Kukho abantu abangaphezu kwama-820 000 abachaphazelekayo kweli lizwe, ngokutsho kwabasebenzi bezempilo.
Kwikota yesibini ka-2018 kuphela, kwafunyaniswa ukuba kukho abantu abangama-40,000 abosulelekileyo.
Inkoliso yamatyala amatsha anokufumaneka ngokwabelana ngesondo, ngokungafaniyo nexesha elidlulileyo.
Ngokwesiko, iHIV yayisasazeka ngokukhawuleza kwezinye iindawo zaseTshayina ngenxa yokutofelwa igazi elosulelekileyo.
Noko ke, inani labantu abafumana iHIV ngenxa yale ngxaki liye lancipha laya kutsho kwixabiso eliphantsi, ngokutsho kwabasebenzi bezempilo baseTshayina kwiinkomfa eziseYunnan.
Noko ke, unyaka nonyaka, inani labantu abaphila neHIV/AIDS eTshayina liye landa ngama-100 000.
Ukudluliselwa kwe-HIV ngokwesondo yingxaki enkulu kuluntu lwe-LGBT lwase China.
I-homosexuality yabekwa phantsi komthetho e-China ngo-1997, kodwa ucalucalulo lwe-LGBT luqhelekile.
Xa kuthathelwa ingqalelo imilinganiselo yokunyaniseka kweli lizwe, uhlolisiso lubonisa ukuba phakathi kwama-70 nama-90% amadoda anesondo lesini esinye aya kugqiba ngokutshata ibhinqa.
Uninzi lwezifo ezidluliselwayo zibangelwa kukungabikho kokhuseleko olufanelekileyo xa ulala nomntu.
Ukususela ngowe-2003, urhulumente waseTshayina uye wathembisa ukuba wonke umntu uza kufumana amayeza okulwa neHIV njengenxalenye yemigudu yakhe yokulwa nale ngxaki.
