UMmeli waseUnited States uMaxine Waters wabhengeza ngeMigqibelo izityholo zokuba ilungu labasebenzi bakhe liye lapapasha iinkcukacha zobuqu zeSenator ezintathu zaseUnited States kwiphepha le-Wikipedia leMithetho.
