Kuthiwa, le nkcazelo yayineedilesi neenombolo zefowuni zeSenator waseMerika uLindsey Graham waseMzantsi Carolina noMike Lee noOrrin Hatch, bobabini baseUtah.
Le nkcazelo yavela kwi-intanethi ngoLwesine yaza yapapashwa ngumntu ongaziwayo eCapitol ngexesha lekomiti yeSenate eyayixubusha ngeengxelo zokuxhatshazwa ngokwesondo kukaBrett Kavanaugh owayefuna ukuba ngumongameli weNkundla Ephakamileyo.
Le ngcaciso yavuza emva kokuba abathathu kwiinkundla zamatyala bebuzile ngoKavanaugh.
Iindawo ezikhuselekileyo, ezinje ngeGateway Pundit kunye neRedState, zaxela ukuba idilesi ye-IP echaza umthombo wezithuba yayixhomekeke kwiofisi kaWaters kwaye yaveza ulwazi lomntu osebenza kuWaters, iCapitol yaxela.
"Esi sityholo singenasizathu sisisiseko sobuxoki yaye sisisiseko sobuxoki", waqhubeka watsho uWaters.
