Uhlalutyo lwe Johnny English Strikes Again: i-parody ye-Limited Spy kaRowand Atkinson
Sele lisiko ukukhangela iimbekiselo zeBrexit kuyo nayiphi na ifilimu entsha enendlela yaseBritane, kwaye le nto iphinda yenziwe ye-franchise ye-comedy-action parody kaJohnny English, eyazalwa ngo-2003 kunye noJohnny English kwaye yavela kwakhona ngo-2011 kunye noJohnny English Reborn, yayingekho ngaphandle.
Ngaba le nto ihlazo yokuziphosa phantsi malunga nokuba singabantu abanjani iya kuba lithuba elitsha lokuthumela ngaphandle ilizwe?
Ngapha koko, uJohnny English ongenabuchule onamehlo aphakamileyo kunye nobuso obunamagqabi uye wakwazi ukuvuselela kwakhona ilayisensi yakhe yesibini yokujika yonke into.
Ngokucacileyo, ngumcebisi oyimfihlakalo, nangona enqabile ukufuna ukubonakala, unento ethile kaClouseau, inqaku likaMnu Bean, kunye nokuthintelwa kwalo mfo, onika inqaku elinye kumxholo weTrakhi yoMlilo kumsitho wokuvula weOlimpiki yaseLondon 2012.
Ekuqaleni, yayisekelwe kumhambi wamazwe ngamazwe kunye nomntu ongaqondakaliyo uAtkinson owayedlala iintengiso zeTV zeBarclaycard, ezazilibalekile ngoku, apho wayeya kubangela isiphithiphithi kuyo yonke indawo.
Kukho umzuzu okanye emibini entle kolu hambo lokugqibela lukaJ.
Wayemthanda uJohnny English owayesondela kwinqwelo-ntaka enxibe isambatho semfazwe esisemaphakadeni yaye amagqabi e-helmet ayexhuma kwikhwelo lakhe.
Uyakwazi ukubona ukuba uAtkinson unetalente yokudlala amahlaya, kodwa umtsalane ubonakala ngathi awunasiphelo kwaye awunasiphelo, ingakumbi kuba iimveliso zefilimu "ezibalulekileyo" ezinje nge-007 kunye neMishini engenakwenzeka ngoku ziquka ikhomidi njengesixhobo.
Ihlaya libonakala lifunwa ngabantwana kunabantu abadala, kwaye kum, iihambo zikaJohnny English ezingaqondakaliyo azikho ngqwabalala okanye zigxile njengamaqhinga athule kaMnu Bean odlala uAtkinson.
Ngoku, into ethethwa rhoqo kukuba iBritani ineengxaki ezinzulu.
Umkhangeli we-computer uye wangena kwinethiwekhi ye-web eyimfihlo yase-Britani waza waveza zonke ii-agents zase-Britani, nto leyo ebangela ukuba i-agent ye-service-service, indima encinci kakhulu kuKevin Eldon, ikhathazeke.
Yinto yokugqibela enokwenziwa nguMphathiswa Omkhulu, obonakala ngathi uyathanda ukuba ngumntu, kwaye sele ehla ngenxa yokungabikho kokuthandwa kwezopolitiko: uEmma Thompson unika okona kulungileyo kuye ngale ndoda ifunyenwe nguTeresa-May, kodwa isicatshulwa asifikeleli apho.
Abacebisi bakhe bezobuntlola bamxelela ukuba, njengoko zonke iimpimpi ezisebenzayo zisengozini, kuya kufuneka abuyisele imali yakhe.
Kwaye oku kuquka uJohnny English ongenabuchule, ngoku usebenza njengotitshala kwiziko elithile lezinto eziphambili, kodwa ufundisa izifundo ezingabhalwanga ngendlela yokuba ngumcebisi, kunye neendlela ezintle, njengokuthi u-English unikezela nge-academy ye-spy eyayinjenge-rock school.
U-English ubuyela ngokukhawuleza e-Whitehall kwintlanganiso engxamisekileyo kunye nomthengisi wakhe we-sequash uBough, indima ephinda idlalwe nguBen Miller.
Ngoku uBough uyindoda etshatileyo, enxulumene nomphathi wenqanawa, indima enomdla, apho uVicky Pepperdine engathandwa.
Ngoko, uBatman noRobin xa izinto ziba mbi kakhulu kwiSebe leNgcaciso likaKumkani baya kuphinda baqalise ukusebenza baze bafumane uOlga Kurylenko, umfazi omangalisayo uOphelia Bulletova.
Okwangoku, lo mphathiswa uphantsi kolawulo lwegosa elinamandla le-technology elizibanga linokuyicombulula ingxaki ye-computer yaseBritani: uJason Volta, omela uJake Lacy.
U-English no-Bough baqala uhambo lwabo lokuhlekisa: begqoke njengabapheki, batshisa indawo yokutyela yaseFransi, bahlazisa abantu besenza izinto ezingekho mthethweni kwi-yacht kaVolta, kwaye u-English wenza isiphithiphithi xa ezama ukusebenzisa isigcina-ntloko se-virtual reality ukuze aqhelane nendawo yokuhlala kaVolta.
Zonke izitishi zivela kweli candelo lokugqibela, kodwa ngenxa yokulula nokungxola kwalo, konke kubonakala ngathi yinkqubo yabantwana.
Izinto eziqhelekileyo.
