Yintoni iGlobal Citizen Festival? Ngaba ikhe yenze nantoni na ukunciphisa ubuhlwempu?
I-New York City izakubamba i-Global Citizen Festival, umnyhadala womculo waminyaka le, ngoMgqibelo, apho kuza kubakho iqela leenkwenkwezi ezibalaseleyo, eziphumeza injongo efanayo: ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu ehlabathini.
Kulo nyaka we-7, iGlobal Citizen Festival iza kubona amashumi amawaka abantu behlanganisana kwindawo yeGreat Lawn e-Central Park kungekuphela nje ukuze bonwabele ukubonakaliswa kukaJanet Jackson, uCardi B noShawn Mendes, kodwa ukuze kuvuswe ulwazi malunga nenjongo yomhlaba wonke yokucima ubuhlwempu obugqithisileyo kwihlabathi ngo-2030.
I-Global Citizen Festival, eyaqala ngo-2012, yongezwa kwi-Global Poverty Project, iqela lehlabathi elifuna ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu ngokunyusa inani labantu abancedisa ukulwa nabo.
Ukuze ufumane itikiti lasimahla (ngaphandle kokuba umntu othile ufuna ukuhlawula itikiti le-VIP), ababekho kwakufuneka benze uthotho lwezinto, njengokuvolontiya, ukuthumela i-imeyile kwinkokeli yehlabathi, ukwenza umnxeba okanye nayiphi na enye into enokunceda ekuqaliseni injongo yokuphelisa ubuhlwempu.
Yintoni eyenziwe yiGlobal Citizen ngoku, ekubeni isele iminyaka eli-12 ukuba ifikelele kwinjongo yayo?
Ingcamango yokunika abantu ikonsathi yasimahla yindlela elungileyo yokubakhuthaza ukuba benze into okanye nje enye into esiyibiza ngokuba "yi-clictivism" (abantu bacinga ukuba yintoni umahluko phakathi kokusayina isicelo kwi-intanethi okanye ukuthumela i-tweet?
Ukususela ngo-2011, iGlobal Citizen ithi ibhale ngaphezu kwe-19 yezigidi "zezenzo" ezenziwe ngabalandeli bayo, eziye zanceda ekufezekiseni iinjongo ezahlukeneyo.
Uthi ezi zenzo ziye zanceda ukukhuthaza iinkokheli zehlabathi ukuba zithethe ngezibophelelo nemigaqo-nkqubo elingana ne-$37 yezigidigidi, eziya kuba nefuthe kubomi babantu abangaphezu kwe-2.250 yezigidigidi ngowama-2030.
Ekuqaleni kuka-2018, eli qela likhankanye izibophelelo ezingama-390 kunye nezibhengezo ezivela kwizabelo zalo, apho ubuncinci i-10.000 yezigidigidi zeedola sele zikhutshelwe okanye zifunyenwe.
Eli qela liqikelela ukuba ngoku iingxowa-mali ezikhuselweyo ziye zachaphazela abantu abaphantse babe zizigidi ezingama-649 ehlabathini lonke.
Ezinye zezinto eziphambili eziye zazibophelela kuzo ziquka iThe Power of Nutrition Foundation, umbutho wabatyali mali kunye nabavelisi abahlala e-UK, abazibophelelayo "ekuncedeni abantwana ukuba bakhule kangangoko kunokwenzeka" kwaye bathembisa ukuthumela i-Rwanda i-35 yezigidi zeedola ukunceda ukulwa ukungondleki kweli lizwe emva kokufumana ii-tweets ezingaphezu kwama-4 700 ezivela kwi-Global Citizens.
"Ngenxa yenkxaso evela kurhulumente wase-UK, abanikeli, oorhulumente bamazwe kunye namalungu e-Global Citizens afana nawe, sinako ukwenza okungekho sikweni kokungondleki kube yinxalenye yebali", uthethe njalo u-Ambassador weThe Power of Nutrition, uTracey Ullman, kwiqela labantu abaphulaphule le nkonzo ngexesha lomnyhadala obakhoyo eLondon ngoAprili 2018.
Eli qela lachaza ukuba emva kwezenzo ezingaphezu kwama-5 000 ezifuna ukuba i-UK iphucule isondlo soomama nabantwana, urhulumente wabhengeza inkxaso-mali yeprojekthi, iThe Power of Nutrition, eya kuthi ifikelele kumabhinqa nabantwana abazizigidi ezi-5 ngeendlela zokutya.
Ukuphendula omnye umqulu we-P+F kwiwebhusayithi yakhe owawubuza "yintoni ekwenza ucinge ukuba singakwazi ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu obugqithisileyo?"
IGlobal Citizen yaphendula yathi: "Kuza kuba nzima kwaye kuza kufuneka sihambe.
Kodwa njengawo onke amaqela amakhulu amalungelo oluntu kunye neqela elichasene nocalulo, siya kuphumelela, kuba xa sisonke somelele.
