I-United States ingasebenzisa i-Navy njenge "blockade" ukuthintela ukuthunyelwa kwe-Russian energy (UMphathiswa wezeNdlu)
IWashington inokusebenzisa amajoni omkhosi wamanzi "ukuba kuyimfuneko" ukuthintela amandla aseRashiya ukuba angawubethi umzi-mveliso, kuquka nezo zikumazwe aseMpuma, utshilo uMphathiswa Wezangaphakathi waseUnited States, uRyan Zinke, njengoko kucatshulwe kwiWashington Examiner.
UZinke uthe ukungenelela kweRashiya eSiriya, ikakhulu apho isebenza khona ngokumenywa ngurhulumente osemthethweni, sisizathu sokufuna iimarike ezintsha zamandla.
