UZinke wayethetha nabantu ababekho kwindibano eyayibanjwe yiConsumer Energy Alliance, iqela elingenzi nzuzo elizibiza ngokuba "lilizwi labathengi bamandla" eMelika.
Wathelekisa iindlela zase Washington zokuthethathethana neRashiya neIran, waza wathi ngokuqinisekileyo ziyafana.
