Umyili weWebhu yeHlabathi jikelele uceba ukwenza i-intanethi entsha ukukhuphisana neGoogle neFacebook
UTim Berners-Lee, umsunguli weWebhu usungula inkampani entsha eza kukhuphisana neFacebook, Amazon neGoogle.
Iprojekthi yokugqibela ye-tech legend, Inrupt, yinkampani esekwe kwiqonga le-solid evulekileyo ka-Berners-Lee.
Iqonga leSolid livumela abasebenzisi ukuba bakhethe apho kugcinwa khona idatha yabo nokuba ngoobani abanokufikelela kulwazi oluthile.
Kudliwanondlebe oluthile neFast Company, uBerners-Lee wahleka esithi injongo efihlakeleyo ye-Inrupt "kukulawula ihlabathi".
"Kufuneka sikwenze ngoku", watsho ethetha ngeshishini elivelayo.
"Eli lixesha eliyimbali".
Isicelo sisebenzisa iteknoloji yeqonga leSolid ukuvumela abasebenzisi ukuba benze "indawo yokugcina idatha kwi-intanethi" okanye i-POD.
Inokuquka uluhlu lwabafowunelwa, uluhlu lwezinto eziza kwenziwa, ikhalenda, ithala lomculo nezinye izixhobo zobuqu nezomsebenzi.
Kufana neGoogle Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, kunye neSpotify. Zonke ziyafumaneka kwi-browser ngaxeshanye.
Into ekhethekileyo yokugcina idatha yakho kwi-intanethi kukuba ngumsebenzisi ogqiba ukuba ngubani onokuthi afikelele kulwazi oluthile.
Le nkampani ithi oku "kukwenza umntu abe namandla ngokusebenzisa idatha".
Ingcamango ye-Inrupt, ngokutsho kwe CEO yenkampani, uJohn Bruce, kukuba inkampani idibanise izixhobo ezifanelekileyo, iinkqubo kunye nobuchule ukuze iqonga leSolid lifumaneke kuwo wonke umntu.
Inkampani ngoku ibunjwa ngu Berners-Lee, Bruce, iqonga lokhuseleko elithengwe yi-IBM, abaphuhlisi abathile kwi-template abaqeshwe ukuba basebenze kwiprojekthi kunye noluntu lwabaqulunqi beenkqubo zokuzithandela.
Ukususela kule veki, abaphuhlisi be-teknoloji kwihlabathi liphela baya kuba nakho ukudala izicelo zabo eziphantsi kwe-Inrupt ngokusebenzisa izixhobo ezikhoyo kwiwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
UBerners-Lee wathi akukho namnye kwiqela lakhe othetha noFacebook noGoogle malunga nokuba kufuneka benze utshintsho olukhulu apho zonke iimodeli zeshishini ziphela ngobusuku.
"Asifuni mvume kubo".
Kwiphepha leMigqibelo kwiMedium, uBerners-Lee wabhala ukuba umsebenzi weInrupt kukubonelela ngamandla orhwebo kunye nenkqubo yokunceda ukukhusela ingqibelelo nomgangatho wewebhu entsha ehlanganiswe kwiqonga leSolid".
Ngowe-1994, uBerners-Lee wayitshintsha i-intanethi xa waseka iWorld Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology.
Kwiinyanga ezidlulileyo, uBerners-Lee ebeligama elinamandla kwingxoxo malunga nokungathathi hlangothi kwe-intanethi.
Nokuba ngexesha lokukhutshwa kwe-Inrupt, uBerners-Lee uya kuqhubeka nokuba ngumseki kunye nomlawuli weWorld Wide Web Consortium, iWorld Wide Web Foundation kunye neOpen Data Institute.
"Ndiqinisekile kakhulu ngeli xesha litsha le-web", wongezelela uBerners-Lee.
