Umphathi-jikelele kunye no-Reverend Bernard Vann wafumana ibhaso ngoSeptemba 29, 1918 ngenxa yokuhlaselwa kweBellenglise neLehaucourt.
Nangona kunjalo, wabulawa ngumpu kwiintsuku ezine kamva kwaye akazange azi ukuba uzuze eyona mbeko ibalulekileyo yaseBritane.
Abantwana bakhe ababini bafumana ilitye lesikhumbuzo kwindibano eyayingoMgqibelo eRushden, eNorthamptonshire.
Omnye wabazukulwana bakhe, uMichael Vann, wathi "kwakungumfuziselo omangalisayo" ukuba ilitye lesikhumbuzo liboniswe kanye kwiminyaka eli-100 emva kokuphumelela kukayisemkhulu.
Ngokutsho kweThe London Gazette, ngoSeptemba 29, 1918, uLieutenant Colonel Vann wakhokela ibhetri yakhe kwiSaint-Quentin Canal "ngentsholongwane enzima kakhulu nangaphantsi komlilo omkhulu wemipu kunye nemitshini yemipu".
