Lo mdlali uphumelele iimbasa ezimbini zeOlimpiki waba ngumkhuthazi ophakamileyo we-LGBT kwaye wasebenzisa umfanekiso wakhe kwiMidlalo ye-Commonwealth kulo nyaka e-Australia ukucela amazwe amaninzi ukuba agxothe ubufanasini.
