Inqanawa entsha yemfazwe yaseJamani, iphinde yahlelwa
I-frigate entsha ye-Army yaseJamani kufuneka igqitywe ngo-2014 ukubuyisela iinqanawa zemfazwe zakudala zexesha leMfazwe ebandayo, kodwa ayizukwenza oko, ubuncinci, kude kube kunyaka olandelayo ngenxa yeenkqubo ezonakeleyo kunye nokunyuka kweendleko, ngokweendaba zasekuhlaleni.
Ukugqitywa kwe-Rheinland-Pfalz, isikhephe esiphambili kwi-Baden-Württemberg-class frigates, iye yahlehliswa ukuya kwisiqingatha sokuqala se-2019, ngokutsho kwephephandaba iDie Zeit, elicaphula isithethi somkhosi.
Inqanawa ibifanele ukuba ingene kwi-Navy ngo-2014, kodwa iingxaki emva kokwakhiwa ziye zenza ukuba le projekthi inqwenelekayo ihambe.
Iinqanawa ezine zeBaden-Württemberg-class ezathunyelwa yiArmy ngo-2007 ziya kuthatha indawo yeefregates zakudala zeBremen.
Kukholelwa ukuba iya kubandakanya umpu onamandla, iseti yeentonga ezichasene nomoya kunye neenkwili, kunye netekhnoloji yokulwa nokugqobhoza, enje nge-radar encinci, infrared kunye nezandla ze-acoustic.
Ezinye iimpawu ezibalaseleyo zibandakanya ixesha elide phakathi kokugcinwa: kufanele ukuba kusetyenziswe ii-frigate ezintsha ukuya kuthi ga kwiminyaka emibini ngaphandle kokudlula kwizibuko lasekhaya.
Nangona kunjalo, ezi zihlandlo zokuqhubeka zibonisa ukuba iinqanawa zangaphambili, ezazibonwa ukuba zinokujolisa eJamani njengamandla amakhulu phesheya, ziya kuba ziphelelwe lixesha xa ziqala ukusebenza, ngokwe Die Zeit.
I-F125 eyayingafunekiyo yayisele iyintshatsheli kunyaka ophelileyo, xa i-Army yaseJamani yalahla inqanawa yaza yabuyela kwi-Blohm & Voss yaseHamburg.
Yayikokokuqala ukuba i-Navy ibuyisele inqanawa kumakhi wayo emva kokuba inikezelwe.
Iinkcukacha ezimbalwa zezizathu zokubuya kwakhe ziyaziwa, kodwa amajelo eendaba aseJamani acaphula "iimpazamo eziphathekayo nezobuchwephesha" zenqanawa ezenza ukuba ingasebenzi ukuba isetyenziswe kwimisebenzi yokulwa.
Iingxaki zobugcisa zibalulekile, kuba malunga nabadobi abali-120, isiqingatha sabasebenzi abafunekayo kwiifregates zakudala zeBremen, zisebenza kwiinqanawa zeBaden-Württemberg.
Ukongeza, kuye kwaziwa ukuba ubunzima benqanawa buninzi, nto leyo inciphisa ukusebenza kwayo kwaye ithintela amandla oMkhosi wezaManzi ukongeza ukuphuculwa kwexesha elizayo.
Kukholelwa ukuba i-Rheinland-Pfalz, yeetoni ezingama-7 000, iya kuba nobunzima obuphindwe kabini kunemikhumbi yeqela elifanayo elisetyenziswe ngamaJamani ngexesha leMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Ngaphandle kwezinto eziphosakeleyo, iindleko zeprojekthi, eziquka uqeqesho lwabasebenzi, nazo ziqala ukuba yingxaki.
Kucingelwa ukuba ifikelele kwii-euro ezingama-3.1 bhiliyoni (iidola ezingama-3.6 bhiliyoni) kwibhajethi yokuqala ye-euro ezingama-2.2 bhiliyoni.
Iingxaki zeenqanawa ezintsha ziye zaba ngumcimbi obaluleke kakhulu, xa kuthathelwa ingqalelo izilumkiso zakutshanje ezibonisa ukuba amandla emikhosi yaselwandle aseJamani ayathotywa.
Kulo nyaka, uHans-Peter Bartels, intloko yeKomiti yoKhuselo yePalamente yaseJamani, uvumile ukuba iArmy s ishiywa ngaphandle kweenqanawa ezinokusetyenziswa.
Igosa lathi imeko iye yaba mandundu ngokuhamba kwexesha kuba iinqanawa zakudala zayekwa ukusetyenziswa, kodwa akukho zintsha zanikelwa njengendawo yokutshintsha.
Uye wazisola ukuba akukho nanye inqanawa yeBaden-Württemberg class enokukwazi ukujoyina uMkhosi.
