UCristiano Ronaldo uthe izityholo zokudlwengulwa kwakhe ziindaba ezingeyonyani kwaye uthi abantu bafuna ukuba nodumo ngenxa yegama lakhe.
Amagqwetha akhe aza kumangalela iphephancwadi laseJamani iDer Spiegel, elinomsebenzi wokupapasha ezi zityholo.
Umdlali weqela lasePortugal neJuventus uye watyholwa ngokudlwengula ibhinqa laseMerika, uKathryn Mayorga, kwigumbi lasehotele eLas Vegas ngowama-2009.
Kuthiwa, wakhupha imali engama-375 000 yeedola ukuze le ngxaki ingabi sesidlangalaleni, ngokutsho kweDer Spiegel ngoLwesihlanu.
Kwividiyo ye-Instagram Live ethetha nabalandeli bakhe abazizigidi ezili-142 kwiiyure emva kokuba izityholo zenziwe zacaca, uRonaldo, oneminyaka engama-33 ubudala, wathi ezi 'ziindaba ezingeyonyani'.
"Hayi, hayi, hayi, hayi.
Oko kuthethwe namhlanje, iindaba ezingeyonyani, kuthethwa ngumntu ophumelele amaxesha amahlanu kwiGolden Ball kwi-cam.
Bafuna ukuba nodumo egameni lam.
Yinto eqhelekileyo.
Bafuna ukusebenzisa igama lam ukuze badume, kodwa yinxalenye yomsebenzi wam.
Ndingumntu onoyolo kwaye yonke into ilungile", wongeze watsho umdlali, encumile.
Amagqwetha kaRonaldo sele elungiselela isimangalo nxamnye neDer Spiegel ngezi zityholo, eziye zachazwa njenge "inkcazelo engavumelekanga ekrokrisayo ngobomi babucala", ngokutsho kweReuters.
Igqwetha uChristian Schertz uthe umdlali uza kufuna imbuyekezo ngenxa yomonakalo wokuziphatha kwinani elihambelana nobunzima bolwaphulo-mthetho, ekusenokwenzeka ukuba lolunye lolona lwaphulo-mthetho lubonakalayo lwamalungelo abantu kwiminyaka yakutshanje.
Esi siganeko sigqugqisileyo senzeka ngoJuni 2009 kwindlu yehotele kunye nekhasino yaseLas Vegas.
Emva kokudibana kwi-nightclub, uRonaldo noMayorga babuyela kwigumbi lomdlali, apho, kuthiwa, wadlwengula, ngokutsho kweengxelo ezifakwe kwiNkundla yeSithili saseClark County, eNevada.
UMajorga uthi uRonaldo waguqa ngamadolo emva kwesi siganeko kwaye wamxelela ukuba uyinkwenkwe elungileyo kwi-99%, ngaphandle kwe-1%.
Amaxwebhu athi uRonaldo waqinisekisa ukuba bobabini babeneentlobano zesini, kodwa bavuma.
UMajorga ukwathe waya emapoliseni waza wathathwa iifoto zamanxeba esibhedlele, kodwa kamva wavuma isivumelwano ngaphandle kweenkundla kuba wayesoyika ukubuyiselwa kwaye wayenexhala lokuba uza kuthotywa esidlangalaleni.
Lo mfazi, oneminyaka engama-34 ubudala, uthi ufuna ukucima isivumelwano, ekubeni ehlala ebuhlungu ngenxa yesiganeko ekuthiwa senzekile.
URonaldo wayesele eza kuthengisa iReal Madrid evela eManchester United ngexesha le ntlekele ekuthiwa yenzekile yaye kule nyanga usayine iJuve, inkampani enkulu yaseItali, ngemali eyi-100 lezigidi zeerandi.
I-Brexit: I-UK Iya kuhlala  izisola ngokulahlekelwa ngabenzi beemoto
I-UK "iya kuzisola ngonaphakade" ukuba ilahlekelwa bubume bayo njengenkokeli yehlabathi kwimveliso emva kweBrexit, ngokutsho kukaGreg Clark, uNobhala wezoQoqosho.
Wongezelela ngelithi "kwakukhathaza" ukuba abasebenzi baseToyota eNgilani baxelele iBBC ukuba, ukuba iUnited Kingdom iyishiya i-European Union ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, iya kuyeka ukuvelisa imveliso kwimizi-mveliso yaseBurnaston, kufuphi neDerby.
"Kufuneka sifikelele kwisivumelwano", watsho uClark.
Umvelisi waseJapan uthe umonakalo obangelwa kukulibaziseka kwemida kwimeko ye-no-deal Brexit unokubangela ukulahleka kwemisebenzi.
Isityalo saseBurnaston, esenza iimodeli zeToyota iAuris neAvensis, ngonyaka ophelileyo savelisa iimoto ezili-150.000, apho ama-90% zithunyelwa kwamanye amazwe e-European Union.
"Ndicinga ukuba, ukuba i-UK iyashiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano ekupheleni kuka-Matshi, imveliso iya kuphazamiseka kumzi-mveliso wethu", utshilo uMarvin Cooke, umphathi weToyota eBurnaston.
Ukuphuma kwe-EU kungekho sivumelwano malunga nendlela urhwebo oluza kusebenza ngayo namanye amazwe e-EU kuye kwavusa uloyiko lwabanye abenzi beemoto base-UK, abanjengoHonda, BMW, Jaguar kunye neLand Rover.
Umzekelo, iBMW ithi izakuvala isityalo seMini eOxford kwinyanga enye emva kweBrexit.
Ezona zinto zixhalabisayo ziquka oko abavelisi bakubonayo njengobungozi kumgca wemveliso xa kukho i-no-deal Brexit.
Umgca wemveliso weToyota wenziwa ngesiseko se "Just in time", kunye namalungu afika rhoqo kwimizuzu engama-37 evela kubathengisi base-UK nase-European Union ukwenza iimoto.
Ukuba i-UK iyashiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano ngo-Matshi 29, kusenokwenzeka ukuba kubekho iziphithiphithi emdeni, oko icandelo lezemveliso likholelwa ukuba kunokubangela ukulibaziseka nokungabikho kwamalungu.
I-Toyota yayingenakukwazi ukugcina izinto zokwenza imveliso ngaphezulu kosuku olunye kwisitya saseDerbyshire, ngokutsho kwenkampani, kwaye imveliso yayiza kufuneka iyekwe ngenxa yoko.
UClark uthi isicwangciso sikaTheresa May seChequers sobudlelwane bexesha elizayo ne-EU "sibekwe ngendlela ecacileyo" ukuze siphephe ezi zikhokelo.
"Kufuneka sifikelele kwisivumelwano. Sifuna ukufumana esona sivumelwano sisiso, njengoko nditshoyo, singasebenzisi nje impumelelo yethu, kodwa sisebenzise ithuba", utshilo kwinkqubo ye-BBC Radio 4 ethi Today.
"Uvavanyo, hayi nje oluvela eToyota, kodwa nakweminye imveliso, lubonisa ukuba kufuneka sikwazi ukuqhubeka neseti yemveliso ephumelelayo".
I-Toyota khange ikwazi ukuqinisekisa ukuba imveliso izakuyekiswa ixesha elingakanani, kodwa, kwixesha elide, ilumkise ngelithi iindleko ezongeziweyo ziya kunciphisa ukhuphiswano lwesityalo kwaye zinokubangela ukulahleka kwemisebenzi.
UPeter Tsouvallaris, osebenze eBurnaston iminyaka engama-24 yaye engumququzeleli weUnited the Union kule ndawo, uthi amalungu aqala ukukhathazeka kakhulu ngale meko: Ngamava, xa ezi zikhundla ziphulukene nawo, akaze abuye
Isithethi sikarhulumente sithi: "Senze isicwangciso esicacileyo nesinokuthenjwa sobudlelwane bethu bexesha elizayo ne-EU".
Ngokutsho kwe-White House, intlanganiso kaTrump noRosenstein inokuhlehliswa kwakhona
Intlanganiso elindelweyo kaDonald Trump noSekela-Mphathiswa WezokuLawula uRod Rosenstein inokuba "yathintelwa kwiveki" njengoko kuqhubeka umlo malunga nomntu oza kuba ngummeli weNkundla ePhakamileyo, uBrett Kavanaugh, ngokutsho kweNdlu eMhlophe ngeCawa.
URosenstein uphethe umsebenzi weGosa eliKhethekileyo uRobert Mueller, ophanda ngongenelelo lwaseRashiya kunyulo, unxibelelwano phakathi kweRashiya kunye noncedo kuTrump kunye nokuthintelwa kobulungisa ngumongameli.
Nokuba uTrump uyamgxotha na ummeli-jikelele wesizwe, aze abeke engozini ukuzimela kukaMueller, oko kuye kwaphakamisa iingxoxo eWashington kangangeenyanga.
Kule nyanga, iNew York Times sele ixele ukuba uRosenstein uxoxe ngethuba lokuthwala imakrofoni ukuze abhale incoko kaTrump kunye nokugxothwa komongameli ngokutshintshwa kwe25th Amendment.
URosenstein uye wakhanyela oko.
Kodwa ngoMvulo odlulileyo waya kwiNdlu ye-White House phakathi kweengxelo zokuba uza kushiya.
Nangona kunjalo, kwabhengezwa ukuba ngoLwesine intlanganiso noTrump, owayeseUnited Nations eNew York.
UTrump uthe angathanda ukuba angamxhasi uRosenstein, kodwa wahlehlisa intlanganiso ukuze angadibani neenkundla zeSenate apho uKavanaugh kunye nomnye wabasetyhini abammangalela ngokwenza kakubi ngokwesondo, uGqr. Christine Blasey Ford, bangqina khona.
NgoLwesihlanu, uTrump wayalela uphando lweveki kwi-FBI malunga nezityholo ezichasene noKavanaugh, nto leyo eyamenza waqhubeka nokulibazisa ukuvota kwiNdlu yoWiso-mthetho.
Umphathiswa weendaba kaTrump uSarah Sanders, wabonakala kwiFox News Sunday.
Xa ebuzwa malunga nentlanganiso kunye noRosenstein, waphendula ngolu hlobo lulandelayo: Akukabekwa mhla, inokuba yile veki, nangona kusenokwenzeka ukuba uya kuba semva kwiveki enye kuzo zonke izinto kunye nenkundla ephakamileyo.
Kodwa siza kubona. Ndihlala ndigcina iindaba zixelwe.
Abanye abavakalisi banokuphikisa oku: USanders akazange enze nasiphi na iseshoni yeendaba ye-White House ukususela ngoSeptemba 10.
Umnxibelelanisi uChris Wallace wabuza ukuba kutheni.
USanders waphendula wathi ukungabikho kweeseshoni zeendaba kwakungenxa yokuba wayengayithandi indlela abachulumancisa ngayo oonondaba kumabonwakude, nangona wathi: "Andiyi kuphika ukuba bayachulumancisa".
Emva koko, wabhekisa ekubeni kuza kwanda unxibelelwano ngqo phakathi kukaTrump kunye neendaba.
"Umongameli wenza iiseshoni ezininzi zemibuzo neempendulo kunaye nawuphi na umongameli wangaphambili", watsho, ngaphambi kokongeza oku kulandelayo ngaphandle kokucaphula umthombo: "Siye sajonga le nkcazelo".
USanders uthe iintlanganiso zeendaba ziyaqhubeka, kodwa ukuba amajelo eendaba anethuba lokubuza umongameli wase-United States ngokuthe ngqo, kungcono kakhulu kunokuthetha nam.
Sizama ukwenza oku kaninzi, nizibonele ngokwenu ukuba sikwenza kaninzi kwezi veki zimbalwa zidlulileyo, kwaye ziya kuthatha indawo yeengxoxo zengxelo xa nibona umongameli wase-United States.
UTrump uphendula imibuzo xa ephuma kwiNdlu yeMhlophe okanye ethatha inxaxheba kwiiseshoni ezivulekileyo okanye kwiingqungquthela zeendaba kunye neenkokheli ezityeleleyo.
Iindibano zeendaba ezizimeleyo aziqhelekanga.
Kule veki eNew York, umongameli usenokuba ubonise ukuba kutheni, emva kokubonakala ngokungekho semthethweni kwaye ngamanye amaxesha engaqhelekanga phambi kweentatheli ezihlanganiseneyo.
UNobhala wezeMpilo ubhalela abasebenzi be-EU kwi-Scottish National Health Service ngenxa yokoyika i-Brexit
UNobhala wezeMpilo ubhale ileta eya kubasebenzi base-EU abasebenza kwi-Scottish National Health Service ukuvakalisa umbulelo wabo kwilizwe labo kwaye unqwenela ukuba baqhubeke emva kwe-Brexit.
UJeane Freeman, ilungu lePalamente yaseScotland, wathumela ileta ngaphantsi kweenyanga ezintandathu emva kokuba iUnited Kingdom ishiye i-EU.
Urhulumente waseScotland sele ezibophelele ekuhlawuleni iindleko zokufaka isicelo sobumi belizwe kubemi base-EU abasebenza kwiinkonzo zikarhulumente ezinikwe igunya.
Kwileta yakhe, uFreeman wabhala oku kulandelayo: "Ehlotyeni, iingxoxo phakathi kwe-UK kunye ne-EU malunga nokuhamba ziye zaqhubeka, kwaye yonke into ibonakala ijolise kwizigqibo ezilindelekileyo eziza kwenziwa kule ntwasahlobo.
Kodwa urhulumente wase-UK naye uqalise amalungiselelo okokuba kungenzeki nto.
Ndiyazi ukuba la ngamaxesha anzima kuni nonke.
Ngoko ke, ndifuna ukuphinda ndixelele ukuba ndiyayixabisa kakhulu inxaxheba yabo bonke abasebenzi, kungakhathaliseki ukuba ngabaluphi na uhlanga.
Abahlobo bethu base-EU, nangaphaya, banikela ngamava kunye nezakhono ezixabisekileyo ezomeleza nokuphucula umsebenzi wethu kwezempilo, ngelixa zinceda izigulana noluntu esilusebenzisayo.
Kakade ke, iSkotlani likhaya lenu, yaye sifuna nihlale kuyo.
UChristion Abercrombie wenza utyando olungxamisekileyo emva kokwenzakala entloko
Umdlali weTennessee State Tigers uChristion Abercrombie uye wafumana utyando olungxamisekileyo emva kokwenzakala entloko ngoMgqibelo kwidabi lama-31-27 nxamnye neVanderbilt Commodores, ngokutsho kukaMike Organ, waseTennessean.
Umqeqeshi weTennessee State uRod Reed uxelele abavakalisi ukuba lo monakalo wenzeke ngaphambi nje kwesiqingatha somdlalo.
"Wafika kumgca wecala waza wawa apho", watsho uReed.
Abaqeqeshi kunye nabasebenzi bezonyango banika uAbercrombie ioksijini kwiqela ngaphambi kokuba bamfake ebhedini baze bamthabathe ukuze bafumane ezinye iimvavanyo.
Igosa laseTennessee State lixelele uChris Harris weWSMV eNashville, eTennessee, ukuba uAbercrombie uphume kwi-O.R. kwiZiko lezeMpilo laseVanderbilt.
UHarris wongeze ukuba "akukho lwazi malunga nohlobo okanye ubungakanani bomonzakalo" kwaye iTennessee State iphando xa umonzakalo wenzeka.
Ngunyaka wokuqala ka-Abercrombie, unyaka wesibini, kunye neTennessee State emva kokubhalisa e-Illinois.
Wayephumeze amanqaku amahlanu ngoMgqibelo ngaphambi kokuba ayeke ukudlala, nto leyo ebangela ukuba abe li-18 kule sizini.
Abathengi bamanye amazwe baya kuhlawula irhafu ephezulu xa bethenga ipropathi e-UK
Abathengi bamanye amazwe baya kuhlawuliswa irhafu ephezulu xa bethenga ipropathi e-UK kunye nemali eyongezelelweyo esetyenziselwa ukunceda abantu abangenamakhaya ngokwezicwangciso ezintsha zeConservative Party.
Oku kuya kuyityeshela impumelelo yeqela likaCorbyn lokutsala abavoti abaselula.
Ukwanda kwerhafu yesitampu kuya kuhlawuliswa kubantu abangabhatalisiyo e-UK.
UHisenda unethemba lokufumana i-120 yezigidi zeefonti ngonyaka ukunceda abantu abangenamakhaya.
Abathengi basemzini kulindeleke ukuba bahlawuliswe irhafu ephezulu xa bethenga impahla e-UK kwaye le mali iza kusetyenziselwa ukunceda abantu abangenamakhaya, inyathelo eliza kubhengezwa nguTheresa May namhlanje.
Esi senzo sijongwa njengenzame yokuthintela impumelelo yentshukumo kaJeremy Corbyn yokutsalela abavoti abaselula ngezithembiso zokubonelela ngezindlu ezifikelelekayo eziza kuchaphazela abo banengeniso ephezulu.
Ukwanda kwerhafu yesitampu kuya kuhlawuliswa kubantu nakwimibutho engakhange ihlawule irhafu e-UK; le mali iya kuhamba kwizenzo zikarhulumente zokulwa namanani abantu abangenamakhaya.
Umthwalo ongaphezulu, oya kongezelelwa kwirhafu yangoku yesitampu, kuquka amanqanaba aphezulu afakwe kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo kwizindlu zesibini kunye nokuqikelela kwezindlu, inokuba yi-3%.
UHisenda ulindele ukufumana imali efikelela kwi-120 yezigidi zeepawundi ngonyaka.
Kuqikelelwa ukuba i-13% yepropati entsha yaseLondon inabantu abangengabo abaseBritani, nto leyo ebangela ukuba amaxabiso anyuke aze abangele ukuba abathengi abatsha bangakwazi ukufikelela kwipropati.
Iindawo ezininzi ezifumileyo kweli lizwe, ingakumbi ikomkhulu, ziye zaba 'zizixeko eziziingxilimbela' ngenxa yabathengi abaninzi basemzini abachitha ixesha elininzi bengekho kweli lizwe.
Eli nyathelo liza kwiiveki emva kokuba uBoris Johnson efune ukuncitshiswa kwerhafu yesitampu ukuze kuncedwe abantu abaselula babe namakhaya abo okuqala.
Watyhola abakhi bezakhiwo ezinkulu ngokugcina amaxabiso epropati ephezulu ngokuthenga umhlaba ngokukhawuleza kwaye ungayisebenzisi, kwaye wabongoza uMay ukuba aphelise iiquotes kwizindlu ezifikelelekayo ukulungisa i- "disaster" yase-Great Britain.
UCorbyn ubhengeze uthotho lweenguqu zezindlu ezicetywayo, ezifana nolawulo lwezindlu kunye nokupheliswa kokugxothwa kwamatyala.
Kwakhona ufuna ukunika iidolophu amandla angakumbi okwakha izindlu ezintsha.
UMay uthe: "Ngenyanga ephelileyo bendithe ndiza kunikezela ixesha lam lokuba ngumongameli ekubuyiseleni iphupha laseBritani: ubomi bufanele bube ngcono kwisizukulwana ngasinye esitsha.
Oko kuthetha ukulungisa imarike yethu yezindlu ezonakeleyo.
IBritani iya kuhlala ivulelekile kuye nabani na ofuna ukuphila, ukusebenza, nokwenza ubomi apha.
Nangona kunjalo, akunakuba kuyinyaniso ukuba kulula kakhulu kubantu abangabemi e-UK, kunye neenkampani ezisekwe phesheya, ukuthenga izindlu xa kuthelekiswa nabemi base-UK abasebenza nzima.
Kwabaninzi, iphupha lokuba nekhaya elikubo likude kakhulu, yaye ukungabi nazindlu kwenza ukuba kube yinto yokwenene.
Jack Ross: "Eyona nto ndiyifunayo kukuqeqesha iScotland"
Umqeqeshi weSunderland uJack Ross uthi eyona nto ayifunayo kukuba ngumqeqeshi weScotland.
Lo mdlali waseScotland, oneminyaka engama-42 ubudala, wamkela umngeni wokuvuselela iqela laseMntla-mpuma, okwangoku elikwindawo yesithathu kwiLeague One, kumathuba amathathu ukusuka kwikhokeli.
Wafika eStadium of Light kweli hlobo emva kokuphinda amise iSt Mirren kwiScotish Premiership kulo nyaka uphelileyo.
Ndandifuna ukudlala kwilizwe lam xa ndandingumdlali.
Ndaye ndabizwa ukuba ndibe ngumxhasi wakhe, utshilo uRoss kwinkqubo yeBBC Scotland ethi Sportsound.
Kodwa ndakhula ndibukela imidlalo emininzi yaseScotland eHampden kunye notata xa ndandisemncinci kwaye ihlala indenza ndibuyele emva kwixesha.
Eli thuba ndiza kulifumana kuphela xa ndiphumelela ekuqeqesheni iiklabhu, kodwa.
Abanduleli bakaRoss kwi-Sunderland njengomqeqeshi baquka uDick Advocaat, uDavid Moyes, uSam Allardyce, uMartin O'Neill, uRoy Keane, uGus Poyet noPaulo Di Canio.
Umqeqeshi wangaphambili weAlloa Athletic uthi akaziva exinzelekile ukuba abe ngowokuqala kuluhlu lwamagama awaziwayo kwiqela elikhulu kangaka, emva kokwala ngaphambili izibonelelo ezivela eBarnsley naseIpswich Town.
Okwangoku, indlela endiza kujonga ngayo impumelelo yam kukuba ndiyakwazi na ukubuyisela eli qela kwiPremier League.
Ngokubhekiselele kulwakhiwo kunye nezixhobo zeqela, kuyacaca ukuba indawo yalo yiPremier League, utshilo.
"Akulula ukufikelela apho, kodwa ndingacinga ukuba ndiphumelele apha ukuba ndinokubuyisela iklabhu".
URoss uneminyaka emithathu kuphela yamava njengomqeqeshi, emva kwexesha njengomqeqeshi wesibini eDumbarton kunye neenyanga ezili-15 kwiqela lobuchwephesha leHearts.
Wanceda iAlloa ukuthintela ukwehliselwa kudidi lwesithathu kwaye waguqula iSt Mirren ukuba ilwele usindiso ibe ziiNtshatsheli zeChampions League kwixesha elilandelayo.
URoss uthi uziva ekhululekile ngoku kunangethuba ebedlala kwiClyde, eHartlepool, eFalkirk, eSt Mirren naseHamilton Academical.
"Mhlawumbi yayilixesha elibalulekileyo", wakhumbula ngokwamkela isikhundla kwiAlloa.
Ndandisoloko ndicinga ukuba ukuqeqesha yinto endinayo, ngaphezu kokudlala.
Kuvakala kumangalisa kuba ndenze kakuhle, ndaphuma kakuhle, ndaza ndanandipha ixesha elimnandi.
Kodwa ukudlala kunokuba nzima kakhulu.
Zininzi izinto ekufuneka uzigqibe veki nganye.
Ndisaqhubeka ndijamelana noxinzelelo noxinzelelo lomsebenzi, kodwa ndiziva ndingumqeqeshi.
Ndandisoloko ndifuna ukuqeqesha, yaye ngoku ndiyakwenza, oku kuye kwaba yeyona nto ndiyiyo ukususela ekubeni ndingumntu omdala.
Unokuyiphulaphula yonke le ngxoxo kwiSportsound ngeCawa, nge-30 kaSeptemba kwiRadio Scotland, phakathi kwentsimbi yeshumi elinesibini ukuya kweyesibini, ixesha lase-UK
Uphando lubonisa ukuba eyona mini ifanelekileyo yokutya ipint ngumgqibelo ngentsimbi yesihlanu ezinesiqingatha.
Ixesha lobushushu lasehlotyeni liye laphakamisa ukusetyenziswa kweebhari ezixinezelekileyo zaseBritani, kodwa kongezelela uxinzelelo kwiinkonzo zokutyela.
Iindawo zokutyela neenkampani zeebhari zonyuse ukuthengiswa kwazo nge-2.7% ngoJulayi, kodwa ukutya kwiindawo zokutyela kwehle nge-4.8%, ngokutsho kwezibalo.
UPeter Martin, we-CGA, inkampani eqokelela le nkcazelo, uthi: "Iiyure eziqhubekayo zokutshiswa kwelanga kunye nokuthatha inxaxheba kweNgilani kwiMidlalo yeHlabathi, eye yathatha ixesha elide kunokuba bekulindelwe, kuye kwabangela ukuba uJulayi alandele indlela efanayo nekaJuni, ekunyuseni i-2,8 ekhulwini kwiivenkile zokutyela, ngaphandle kweendawo zokutyela, eziye zafumana ubunzima obungakumbi.
Ukwehla kwe-1.8% kwisitya sokutya kwisitya sokutya ngoJuni kuye kwaphazamiseka ngoJulayi.
Iindawo zokutyela, eziphambili kwiziselo, ziye zafumana ezona ziphumo ziphezulu, ngelixa ukutya kwiivenkile zokutyela kuye kwehla.
Iindawo zokutyela nazo ziye zafumana umonakalo elangeni, nangona zingakhange zibe nzima kangako njengendawo zokutyela.
Kubonakala ngathi abantu babefuna nje ukuphuma baze basele.
