Iinyikima neetsunami eIndonesia
Abantu abangama-384 babulawa yinyikima enkulu kunye netsunami ezithe zantlitha isixeko saseIndonesia iPalu ngolwesiHlanu, ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni.
Ngenxa yokuba unxibelelwano luvaliwe, amaqela okunceda akakwazanga ukufumana ulwazi kwi-Donggala Regency, indawo ekumantla ePalu kufutshane nendawo ekungene kuyo inyikima enkulu.
EPalu, abantu abangaphezu kwe-16 000 baye bagxothwa emva kwale ntlekele.
Nazi ezinye iinkcukacha ezibalulekileyo malunga nePalu neDonggala, kwiCelebes Island:
IPalu likomkhulu lephondo laseCelebes Central, elisecaleni kwebhadi emxinwa kunxweme olusentshona lwesiqithi saseCelebes, elinabemi abaqikelelwa kuma-379,800 ngonyaka ka-2017.
Esi sixeko sasibhiyozela iminyaka engama-40 xa inyikima netsunami zantlitha.
I-Donggala yindawo ekumantla-ntshona weCelebes.
I-regency, ingingqi yolawulo engaphantsi kwephondo, yayinabantu abamalunga nama-299,200 ngo-2017.
Ukuloba kunye nezolimo ziziseko zoqoqosho kwiPhondo laseCelebes eliPhakathi, ingakumbi kwingingqi yonxweme yaseDonggala.
Ukusetyenziswa kwemigodi ye-nickel nayo ibalulekile kwiphondo, kodwa igxile, ikakhulu, eMorowali, kunxweme kwelinye icala leCèlebes.
IPalu neDonggala ziye zathwaxwa ziitsunami ezininzi kwiminyaka eli-100 edluleyo, ngokutsho kwe-arhente yokunciphisa iintlekele eIndonesia.
Ngowe-1938, itsunami yabulala abantu abangaphezu kwama-200 yaza yatshabalalisa amakhaya amaninzi eDonggala.
Ngowe-1996 kwabakho itsunami kwintshona yeDonggala eyabulala abantu abasithoba.
I-Indonesia ikwiPasifiki, yaye iququququ zidla ngokwenzeka.
Ezi zilandelayo ziquka iinyikima ezinkulu neetsunami zeminyaka yakutshanje:
NgoDisemba 26, 2004 - Inyikima enkulu kunxweme olusentshona yephondo laseIndonesia iAce, kumntla weSumatra, yabangela itsunami eyachaphazela amazwe ali-14 yaza yabulala abantu abangama-226 000 kunxweme lweIndiya, ngaphezu kwesiqingatha sabo eAceh.
2005: Iinyikima ezinkulu zothusa unxweme olusentshona yeSumatra ekupheleni kukaMatshi nasekuqaleni kukaAprili.
Amawaka abantu afa kwisiqithi saseNias, kunxweme lwaseSumatra.
Ngowe-2006 inyikima enkulu enamandla angama-6.8 yahlasela uMzantsi weJava, esona siqithi sinabantu abaninzi eIndonesia, yaza yabangela itsunami eyahlasela unxweme olusemazantsi yaza yabulala abantu abaphantse babe yi-700.
Ngowama-2009: Inyikima enkulu eyayimalunga ne-7.6 yazamazamisa indawo ekufutshane nesixeko sasePadang, ikomkhulu lephondo laseNtshona Sumatra.
Kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwe-1 100.
Ngowe-2010: Inyikima enkulu engange-7.5 yazamazamisa isiqithi saseMentawai, kunxweme lwaseSumatra, yaza yabangela itsunami engangeemitha ezili-10 eyabhukuqa iilali ezininzi yaza yabulala abantu abamalunga nabayi-300.
2016: Inyikima encinci yahlasela iPidie Jaya Regency e-Aceh yaza yabangela ukonakaliswa kunye nexhala, njengoko abantu bakhumbula umonakalo owabangelwa yinyikima kunye netsunami ngo-2004.
Kule meko, akuzange kubekho tsunami, kodwa kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwe-100 ngenxa yokugqabhuka kwezakhiwo.
Ngo-2018: Kwenzeka iinyikima ezinkulu kwisiqithi saseIndonesia, eLombok, ezibulala abantu abangaphezu kwe-500, abaninzi bebulawa kumntla wesiqithi.
Le nyikima yatshabalalisa amawaka ezakhiwo yaza yashiya amawaka abakhenkethi bexakeke okwethutyana.
Unyana kaSara Palin omdala ubanjwe ngetyala lobundlobongela basekhaya
UTrack Palin, unyana omkhulu wenguMongameli we-Alaska kunye nomviwa kwi-Vice-President uSarah Palin, ubanjwe ngecala lokuhlaselwa.
UPalin, oneminyaka engama-29 ubudala, ovela eWasillah, eAlaska, wabanjwa ngenxa yokuba ethandabuza ubundlobongela basekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yobundlobongela basekhaya nokumelana nokubanjwa, ngokutsho kwengxelo ekhutshwe ngoMgqibelo yiAlaska State Troopers.
Ngokutsho kwengxelo yamapolisa, xa umntu amthandayo wazama ukufowunela amapolisa ukuze achaze ulwaphulo-mthetho, waphakamisa ifowuni yakhe.
UPalin ubanjwe kwiziko lokugcinwa kwabantu kwilizwe laseMat-Su, apho agcinwe khona ngexabiso elingenasiqinisekiso elingange-500 USD, ngokutsho kweKTUU.
Wavela enkundleni ngoMgqibelo, xa wavakalisa "ukuba akanatyala, ngokuqinisekileyo" xa ebuzwa ukuba uthini, ngokutsho kwale nethiwekhi.
UPalin ujamelene neentlobo ezintathu zokwaphula umthetho, nto leyo ethetha ukuba unokutyalelwa entolongweni kangangonyaka aze ahlawule isohlwayo esifikelela kwi-250.000 USD.
Ukwatyholwa ngesiphoso esikumgangatho B, esinokujeziswa ngentsuku enye entolongweni kunye ne-$2,000 (i-R70.000) yentlawulo.
Akusayiyo okokuqala ukuba uPalin abekwe izityholo zolwaphulo-mthetho.
NgoDisemba 2017 watyholwa ngokubetha utata wakhe, uTodd Palin.
Umama wakhe, uSarah Palin, wabiza amapolisa ukuze achaze ukuhlaselwa kwakhe.
Ngoku, eli tyala lisezandleni zenkundla yabadala baseAlaska.
NgoJanuwari 2016 watyholwa ngokuhlaselwa ekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yolwaphulo-mthetho lwendlu kunye nokuba nompu xa etywala ngokunxulumene nesiganeko.
Umlingane wakhe wavuma ukuba umbethe ebusweni.
Ngowe-2016, uSarah Palin wagxekwa ngamaqela amajoni omkhosi ngenxa yokudibanisa ukuziphatha kwakhe ngogonyamelo kunye ne-PTSD evela kwinkonzo yakhe e-Iraq.
