Abatshutshisi baseRiphabhlikhi bacela isigwebo sentambo esingaqhelekanga kwisityholo sokubethwa kwabantu kwiNew York
Abatshutshisi baseNew York bafuna isigwebo sentambo kuSayfullo Saipov, umntu okrokrelekayo ekuhlaseleni abantu eNew York okwatshayela abantu abasibhozo: isigwebo esingaqhelekanga esingazange sinikwe urhulumente ngenxa yolwaphulo-mthetho lukazwelonke ukususela ngowe-1953.
USaipow, oneminyaka engama-30 ubudala, kuthiwa wasebenzisa imoto eqeshiswe yiHome Depot ukuze ahlasele ibhayisekile eWest Side Highway, eLower Manhattan waza wabetha abantu abahamba ngeenyawo nabakhweli bamabhayisekile endleleni ngo-Oktobha.
Ukuze bafumane isigwebo sokufa, abameli kufuneka babonise ukuba uSaipov wabulala aba bantu basibhozo "ngokunyamekela" yaye "ngokunyamekela" wabangela ukwenzakala okukhulu, ngokutsho kweSaziso Sokufuna Ukufa kwiSithili saseMzantsi weNew York.
Omabini la matyala anokufaka isigwebo sokufa, ngokutsho kwexwebhu lenkundla.
Kwiiveki emva kokuhlaselwa, ijaji enkulu yaseburhulumenteni yahlasela uSaipov ngecala elinamaphutha angama-22 kuquka amatyala asibhozo okubulala abantu ukuze kuxhamle ulwaphulo-mthetho olulungelelanisiweyo, oludla ngokusetyenziswa ngabatshutshisi abaseburhulumenteni kwimeko yamaqela amaKhomanisi, kunye nelinye ityala lobundlobongela nokutshatyalaliswa kwezithuthi.
Abatshutshisi bathi ukuhlaselwa kwafuneka "kucetywe kakuhle" yaye bachaza indlela uSaipov awayeziphatha ngayo "njengokungabi naluntu, okhohlakeleyo nokungekho sikweni".
"USayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov wabangela ukwenzakala, umonakalo kunye nelahleko kwiintsapho kunye nabahlobo bakaDiego Enrique Angelini, uNicholas Cleves, uAnn-Laure Decadt, uDarren Drake, uAriel Erlij, uHernan Ferruchi, uHernan Diego Mendoza noAlejandro Damian Pagnucco", ngokutsho kwesibhengezo senjongo.
Amahlanu kula maxhoba yayingabakhenkethi baseArgentina.
Sele kudlule ishumi leminyaka ukususela kwixesha lokugqibela iSouthern District yaseNew York yazisa ityala lokufa.
Ummangalelwa, uKhalid Barnes, wagwetywa ngokubulala abaxhasi beziyobisi ababini, kodwa ekugqibeleni wagwetywa ubomi entolongweni ngoSeptemba 2009.
Isigwebo sokufa sagqitywa okokugqibela kwityala laseNew York lika-1953 kuJulius noEthel Rosenberg, isibini esitshatileyo esabulawa emva kokugwetywa ngenxa yokuceba ukwenza umsebenzi wokuhlola iSoviet Union ngexesha leMfazwe ebandayo kwiminyaka emibini ngaphambili.
Bobabini uRosenbergs basweleka kwisitulo sombane ngoJuni 19, 1953.
Ngokutsho kweencwadi zenkundla, uSaipov, ozalwa eUzbekistan, akazange abonise inguquko kwiintsuku neenyanga emva kokuhlaselwa.
Amapolisa athi waxelela abaphandi ukuba wayeziva emkelekile ngento awayeyenzile.
Ngokutsho kwe-impeachment, uSaipov uchazele abasemagunyeni ukuba waphefumlelwa ukuba enze lo mhlalutyo emva kokubona iividiyo ze-ISIS kwifowuni yakhe.
Ngokutsho kwamapolisa, wacela ukuba iflegi ye-ISIS ifakwe kwigumbi lakhe esibhedlele.
Uye wavuma ukuba akanatyala kwizityholo zokungaphumeleli kwezi 22.
UDavid Patton, omnye wabaxhasi bakarhulumente abaseburhulumenteni abamele uSaipov, wathi "ngokusobala baphoxekile" sisigqibo sesityholo.
"Sicinga ukuba isigqibo sokufuna isigwebo sentambo, endaweni yokwamkela isigwebo sobugwenxa kunye nokuvalelwa ubomi bonke ngaphandle kokukhululeka kuya kuqhubeka nokubuhlungu kwezi ziganeko kubo bonke ababandakanyekayo", utshilo uPatton.
Iqela elijongene nokukhusela uSaipov lalicel' umngeni ngaphambili ukuba abavakalisi bangasifuni isigwebo sokufa.
Ilungu lePalamente leqela elilawulayo lithi uNIGEL FARAGE kufuneka abekwe ukuba abe ngumphathi weentetho zeBrexit
UNigel Farage uthembise "ukuqokelela imikhosi yabantu" namhlanje ngexesha lokubonisa inkxaso kwinkomfa yeqela leConservative.
Inkokeli yangaphambili ye-UKIP ithe abezopolitiko kufuneka "bazive bephantsi koxinzelelo lwabantu abachasayo i-euro" xa ilungu lePalamente likaTheresa May licebise ukuba kufuneka likhokele iingxoxo ne-EU.
I-MP engekhoyo, uPeter Bone, wathi kwi-Birmingham March ukuba i-UK yayiza kuba ngaphandle kwe-EU ukuba uMnu Farage ebeyi-Secretary of Brexit.
Kodwa umngeni uMama May ajongene nawo ekuxolelaniseni amaqela akhe ahlukeneyo wabonakala xa amaqela aseleyo e-Union aye abonisa inkxalabo yawo kwiqela eliphikisayo iBrexit eLa City.
Inkulumbuso isilwa ukuze igcine isicwangciso sayo sokuzibophelela seChequers phakathi kokuhlaselwa ngabalandeli beBrexit, abaxhasi be-union kunye ne-EU.
Amaqabane agxininisa ukuba uza kukwazi ukufikelela kwisivumelwano neBrussels nangona iimpendulo zingekhoyo kwaye uxinzelelo kwii-euro-sceptics kunye neqela le-conservative ukuba bakhethe phakathi kwephakheji yabo kunye nesiphithiphithi.
UMnu Bone uxelele intlanganiso yaseSolihull ethi iLeave Means Leave ukuba ufuna ukuyikhulula i-Chequers.
Uthe uMnu Farage bekufanele ukuba ubekwe kwiNdlu yeeNdlu zeNdlu kwaye kufuneka anikwe uxanduva lokuthetha-thethana neBrussels.
'Ukuba ebesongamele, besingaphaya,' watsho.
IPalamente yaseWellingborough yongezelela yathi: "Ndiza kuyikhusela iBrexit, kodwa kufuneka siyisuse into eyenziwe nguChequers".
