Indlela US-China imfazwe yorhwebo inokuba kuzuza Beijing
Iintlekele zokuqala zemfazwe yorhwebo phakathi kwe-US ne-China zazinzima, kwaye nangona imfazwe ingakhange ibonakale ngathi iphela ngokukhawuleza, ukuhlukana kwamazwe kunokuba luncedo eBeijing kwixesha elide, ngokutsho kweengcali.
UMongameli waseUnited States uDonald Trump, wenza isilumkiso sakhe sokuqala ekuqaleni konyaka, xa wafaka irhafu kwizinto eziphambili ezithunyelwa ngaphandle eTshayina, ezinjengeepaneli zelanga, intsimbi nealuminiyam.
Eyona nto ibalulekileyo eyenzekayo kule veki, kukuhlawuliswa kweerhafu ezintsha kweemveliso ezixabisa i-200 yezigidigidi zeedola, ezihlawuliswa kwihafu yazo zonke iimpahla eziza eMelika zivela eChina.
I-Beijing iye yaziphindezela ngokufanayo, kutshanje inyuse amaxabiso e-US ukusuka kwi-5 ukuya kwi-10 pesenti kwi-60 yezigidigidi zeedola zeempahla zaseMelika.
I-China izimisele ukukopa i-United States kwaye ayinakwenzeka ukuba ibe lilizwe lesibini ngobukhulu kwezoqoqosho ukuba libuyele umva.
Ukwenza iWashington ukuba ibuye umva kuthetha ukuyekelela kwiimfuno ezithile, kodwa ukuqubuda esidlangalaleni eMelika kuya kuba lihlazo kakhulu kuXi Jinping, uMongameli waseTshayina.
Noko ke, iingcali zithi, ukuba iBeijing idlala kakuhle, ingcinezelo yemfazwe yorhwebo neUnited States inokuyinceda iChina ekudambiseni ukuxhomekeka kwezoqoqosho.
UAbhigali Grace, umcebisi weAsia kwiCenter for New American Security uthi: "Ukuba umgaqo-nkqubo okhawulezileyo waseWashington okanye waseBeijing unokubangela ukuba kubekho iimeko ezibangela ukuba elo lizwe liwe, kuyingozi kakhulu kunokuba bekucingelwa ngamangqina".
