I-USA sele ilahlekelwe izihlandlo ezithandathu zilandelelana eYurophu kwaye ayiphumelelanga kwiRyder Cup eYurophu ukusukela ngo-1993.
Iqela laseYurophu laphinda laphumelela xa iqela likaputeni waseDenmark uThomas Bjorn lafikelela kumanqaku ali-14,5 afunekayo ukuze liphumelele iUnited States.
Inkwenkwezi yaseMelika uPhil Mickelson, owayesilwa uninzi lwetheminali, waphosa isibhamu sokuphuma emanzini kumngxuma we-3 16, nto leyo eyabangela ukuba uFrancesco Molinari aphumelele.
Umdlali wegalufa waseItali uMolinari waqaqamba kuzo zonke iitumente zakhe waza waba ngomnye wabadlali abane abaphumelele kwi-5-0-0 ukusukela oko kwaqala ifomathi yangoku ye-tournament ngo-1979.
UmMerika uJordan Spieth wabekelwa bucala nge-5&4 ngumdlali ongakhange afaneleke kwiqela laseYurophu uThorbjorn Olesen, waseDenmark.
