"Ndiyazingca ngokumfumana uTiger Woods, ndakhula ndimlandela", watsho uRahm, oneminyaka engama-23 ubudala.
UWoods waphulukana nemidlalo yakhe emine eFransi kwaye ngoku unerekhodi yobomi kwiRyder Cup ye-13-21-3.
Eli linani elingaqhelekanga lomnye wabadlali ababalaseleyo, owakhe waphumelela amaqonga amakhulu ali-14 yaye usemva nje kukaJack Nicklaus.
Iqela laseMerika lalilwela yonke le mpelaveki ukuze lifumane iindawo, ngaphandle kukaPatrick Reed, uJustin Thomas noTony Finau, ababedlala igalufa ekumgangatho ophezulu kulo lonke eli qela.
UKaputeni waseMerika uJim Furyk wathetha emva kokudana kweqela lakhe esithi: "Ndiyazingca ngala mdlali, baye balwa.
Kwakukho ixesha ngale ntsasa apho sasinyanzelisa ukhetho lwaseYurophu.
Siye salwa.
Ndiyayicaphukela uThomas.
Ungumphathi omkhulu.
Abadlali bayo abali-12 badlale kakuhle kakhulu.
Siza kuhlangana kwakhona, sisebenze ne-PGA yaseMelika kunye neKomiti yethu yeRyder Cup kwaye siya kwenza inkqubela.
Ndibathanda kakhulu aba badlali bali-12 yaye ndiziva ndinelunda ngokuba ngumphathi wabo.
Kufuneka ususe i-sweat.
Siye saphulukana".
Ukuhlaziywa kwe-Red Tide: Ukuxinana kwehla ePinellas, eManatee naseSarasota
Ingxelo yakutshanje yeFlorida Fish and Wildlife Commission ibonisa ukuncitshiswa ngokubanzi kweenqanaba ezibomvu kwiinxalenye ezithile zendawo yaseTampa Bay.
Ngokutsho kweFWC, iimeko zokwanda ezilahliweyo ziyaxelwa kwiindawo zasePinellas, eManatee, eSarasota, eCharlotte naseCollier, nto leyo ebonisa ukuba umlinganiselo wokwanda awukho mde.
Ukuxhaphaka kwe-red tide kunwenwela kumgama omalunga neekhilomitha ezingama-200 kunxweme, ukusuka kumantla ePinellas ukuya kumazantsi e-Lee.
Amabala afumaneka kumgama weekhilomitha ezili-10 kunxweme lwaseHillsborough, kodwa kwiindawo ezimbalwa, xa kuthelekiswa nemeko yeveki ephelileyo.
I-Red Tide ikwabonwa kwi-Pasco County.
Kukho iingxelo zeenxinano eziphakathi kunxweme okanye kude nonxweme ePinellas County kwiveki ephelileyo, iziganeko eziphantsi ukuya phezulu kunxweme kwiHillsborough County, iziganeko eziphantsi okanye eziphezulu kwiManatee County, iziganeko eziphakathi kwezantsi eCharlotte County, iziganeko eziphantsi ukuya phezulu kunxweme okanye kude nonxweme eLee County, neziganeko eziphantsi kwiCollier County.
Ukuphazamiseka komoya kuyaqhubeka ukuboniswa kwiiPinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee naseCollier.
Akukho nto ibikwayo yokuxinezeleka komoya kule veki iphelileyo kumntla-mpuma weFlorida.
